NK048(tshi)001:1: // nges shes rin po che'i sgron me bzhugs so //
NK048(tshi)001:2: gang yid the tshom d+r+wa ba'i sbubs 'thums pa //
NK048(tshi)001:3: 'byed byed 'jam dpal rdo rje'i mar me ni //
NK048(tshi)001:4: snying la nges shes zab mo'i tshul 'jug pa //
NK048(tshi)001:5: lam bzang mthong ba'i mig der bdag kyang dad //
NK048(tshi)001:6: kye ma zab mo'i gnas lugs la //
NK048(tshi)001:7: sbyor byed nges shes rin po che //
NK048(tshi)001:8: khyod med pas na srid pa 'di //
NK048(tshi)001:9: sgyu ma'i rgyar ni 'thums shing rmongs //
NK048(tshi)001:10: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i chos rnams la //
NK048(tshi)001:11: nges pas yid ches 'drong ba dang //
NK048(tshi)001:12: thos pas dad par byed pa gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:13: lam dang de yi gzugs brnyan bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:14: rmad byung chos kyi zla ba'i grags pa ni //
NK048(tshi)001:15: legs bshad gsung gi 'od dang chab cig par //
NK048(tshi)001:16: thub bstan lha lam yangs por shar ba yis //
NK048(tshi)001:17: the tshom mun pa thib po rnam par 'joms //
NK048(tshi)001:18: tha snyad dpyod pa'i tshad ma yis //
NK048(tshi)001:19: blang dong 'jug ldog mi nor zhing //
NK048(tshi)001:20: khyad par bstan dang ston pa la //
NK048(tshi)001:21: yid ches rnyed pa'i sgo gcig pu //
NK048(tshi)001:22: tshad ma'i gzhung dang gnas lugs don //
NK048(tshi)001:23: gtan 'bebs don dam rig shes kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:24: tshad ma dri med gsal byed pa //
NK048(tshi)001:25: theg mchog dbu ma rnam pa gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:26: legs par sbyangs pa'i blo mig zung //
NK048(tshi)001:27: bgrad de ston pas bstan pa'i lam //
NK048(tshi)001:28: der ni gzhan dring mi 'jog par //
NK048(tshi)001:29: yang dag zhugs pa de la basngagasa //
NK048(tshi)001:30: de ltar sems pa'i drang srong la //
NK048(tshi)001:31: thol byung sdom bu pa zhig gis //
NK048(tshi)001:32: rtog ge'i brgal brtag bya ba'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:33: dri ba bdun po 'di ltar dris //
NK048(tshi)001:34: gzhan gyi rjes su zlos la mkhas pas ci //
NK048(tshi)001:35: rang gi rnam par dpyod pa bag phob la //
NK048(tshi)001:36: dris ba'i lan 'di nye bar ldon mdzod dang //
NK048(tshi)001:37: nang gi rnam dpyod mthong ba bzhin du gsal //
NK048(tshi)001:38: mang thos sna zhags ring du brkyang na yang //
NK048(tshi)001:39: khron pa'i chu ltar zab pa'i chos kyi chu //
NK048(tshi)001:40: ma myong da rung mkhas pa'i grags pa la //
NK048(tshi)001:41: re ba rigs ngan btsun mor chags dang 'dra //
NK048(tshi)001:42: lta ba dgag gnyis gang ltar smra //
NK048(tshi)001:43: nyan rang bdag med gnyis rtogs sam //
NK048(tshi)001:44: mnyam bzhag 'dzin stangs yod dam med //
NK048(tshi)001:45: dpyad nas bsgom mam bzhag nas bsgom //
NK048(tshi)001:46: bden pa gnyis las gang zhig gtso //
NK048(tshi)001:47: mi gcig mthun snang blta bya gang //
NK048(tshi)001:48: dbu mar khas len yod dam med //
NK048(tshi)001:49: de skad stong nyid las brtsams pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:51: lung dang bgal ba med bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:52: rigs pas grub pa'i lan thongs shig /
NK048(tshi)001:53: rtog ge'i tshig phreng tshir ma'i mdung //
NK048(tshi)001:54: 'bum gyis bsnub kyang mi phig pa //
NK048(tshi)001:55: che rnams rmongs pa'i dka' gnad la //
NK048(tshi)001:56: smra ba'i ljags ring glog bzhin rkyongs //
NK048(tshi)001:57: de ltar blo gros kyis bskul ngag gi rlung //
NK048(tshi)001:58: chung ngur g.yos pa des kyang drang srong snying //
NK048(tshi)001:59: dus mtha'i rlung gis ri bzhin bsgul gyur nas //
NK048(tshi)001:60: mi smra'i brtul zhugs dar gcig bzung ba'i mthar //
NK048(tshi)001:61: kye ma brgya phrag dka' ba'i khur brten cing //
NK048(tshi)001:62: yang dang yang dpyad blo gros rnon po'i me //
NK048(tshi)001:63: brgyud mar ches cher sbar ba des kyang 'di //
NK048(tshi)001:64: skyon bral khams su bsgrub par mi nus na //
NK048(tshi)001:65: lhan skyes spobs pa'i blo nus zhan gyur cing //
NK048(tshi)001:66: yun ring sbyangs pa'i khur kyang ma bzung ba //
NK048(tshi)001:67: dman pa bdag gis smra ba ga la zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:68: 'jam pa'i dbyangs la gdung ba'i shugs kyis bos //
NK048(tshi)001:69: de tshe de yi mthu las yin snyam pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:70: yid la tho reng dus kyi snang ba ltar //
NK048(tshi)001:71: spobs pa'i go skabs cung zad thob pa'i mod //
NK048(tshi)001:72: legs gsung don bzhin rigs pas dpyad de smras //
NK048(tshi)001:73: dge ldan lta ba med dgag zer //
NK048(tshi)001:74: gzhan rnams ma yin dgag tu smra //
NK048(tshi)001:75: snga 'gyur ring lugs gang zhe na //
NK048(tshi)001:76: zung 'jug ye shes chen po'i ngor //
NK048(tshi)001:77: med ces dgag bya bkag shul gyi //
NK048(tshi)001:78: med rkyang dang ni ma yin zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:79: bkag shul chos gzhan ci zhig 'phen //
NK048(tshi)001:80: de gnyis blo yis brtag pa tsam //
NK048(tshi)001:81: don la gnyis kar khas mi len //
NK048(tshi)001:82: dgag sgrub gnyis dang bral ba yi //
NK048(tshi)001:83: blo 'das gdod ma'i chos nyid yin //
NK048(tshi)001:84: stong tshul kho nar bsams nas ni //
NK048(tshi)001:85: dri na med dgag nyid yin te //
NK048(tshi)001:86: 'phags yul dpal ldan zla ba dang //
NK048(tshi)001:87: bod na rong zom chos bzang gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:88: dgongs pa gcig dang dbyangs gcig gis //
NK048(tshi)001:89: ka dag stong pa chen po bsgrubs //
NK048(tshi)001:91: gdod nas rang bzhin med pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:92: bden pa gnyis char ma skyes pas //
NK048(tshi)001:93: med ces brjod la ci zhig tshom //
NK048(tshi)001:94: ka ba ka nas dag pa yi //
NK048(tshi)001:95: shul na mi stong cung zad med //
NK048(tshi)001:96: ka ba med ces ma bkag na //
NK048(tshi)001:97: ka ba min zhes ci zhig yin //
NK048(tshi)001:98: ka ba kheg pa'i stong pa dang //
NK048(tshi)001:99: shul na lus pa'i snang ba gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:100: stong dang ma stong zung 'jug tu //
NK048(tshi)001:101: mi rung srad bu sgrim pa bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:102: ka ba ka bas mi stong dang //
NK048(tshi)001:103: chos nyid ka bas stong ngo zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:104: stong gzhi bzhag nas gzhan stong pa //
NK048(tshi)001:105: tshig dang don gyi gzhan stong gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:106: e ma des de ma stongs na //
NK048(tshi)001:107: stong gzhi mi stong lhag mar lus //
NK048(tshi)001:108: gzugs ni gzugs kyis stong ngo zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:109: lung don rigs par bcas las 'gal //
NK048(tshi)001:110: ka ba ka ba'i bden grub gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:111: gcig na gcig kheg gcig kyang kheg /
NK048(tshi)001:112: gzhan na ka ba ma yin pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:113: bden grub kheg kyang ka ba ni //
NK048(tshi)001:114: gang gis mi stong dpyad bzod 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:115: bden grub yod ma myong ba'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:116: gcig dang tha dad mi dgos na //
NK048(tshi)001:117: bden grub med kyang so skye'i ngor //
NK048(tshi)001:118: bum pa bden par 'dzin pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:119: mi stong bum pa'i pha rol na //
NK048(tshi)001:120: bden par grub rgyu su zhig yin //
NK048(tshi)001:121: dgag bya'i snang tshul nges so lo //
NK048(tshi)001:122: bden grub sogs kyi khyad par gang //
NK048(tshi)001:123: dgag byar sbyar nas ston pa ni //
NK048(tshi)001:124: rang rgyud gzhung la grags mod kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:125: don dam dpyod pa'i dbang du na //
NK048(tshi)001:126: de sbyar ba la dgos pa ci //
NK048(tshi)001:127: stong na kun rdzob tsam du yang //
NK048(tshi)001:128: ka ba med pa ltar sems nas //
NK048(tshi)001:131: kun rdzob tsam du ka ba ni //
NK048(tshi)001:132: yod ces byas pas mi chog par //
NK048(tshi)001:133: des de mi stong ci la zer //
NK048(tshi)001:134: de gnyis don gcig yin zer na //
NK048(tshi)001:135: ma yin ka ba yod ces dang //
NK048(tshi)001:136: ka bar ka ba yod ces pa //
NK048(tshi)001:137: mi mtshungs phyi ma rten brten par //
NK048(tshi)001:138: don gyi khas blangs song ba bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:139: don dam ka ba mi dmigs na //
NK048(tshi)001:140: ka ba ka bas mi stong ci //
NK048(tshi)001:141: kun rdzob ka ba ka bas zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:142: lan gnyis brjod pa brda' la rmongs //
NK048(tshi)001:143: rang ni rang gis mi stong na //
NK048(tshi)001:144: rang yod bzhin du gzhan gyis stong //
NK048(tshi)001:145: dgag bya gzhan du med gyur na //
NK048(tshi)001:146: rang gis mi stong khas len 'gal //
NK048(tshi)001:147: spyir na gzhan gyis stong pa des //
NK048(tshi)001:148: stong go nges par mi chod de //
NK048(tshi)001:149: rta la ba lang ma grub kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:150: rta de stong bar ga la nges //
NK048(tshi)001:151: rta mthong de yis ba lang la //
NK048(tshi)001:152: ci zhig phan te ci zhig gnod //
NK048(tshi)001:153: de phyir mi stong myang 'das dang //
NK048(tshi)001:154: 'khor ba'ang chos dang chos nyid du //
NK048(tshi)001:155: mi rung snang stong zung 'jug dang //
NK048(tshi)001:156: srid zhi mnyam nyid 'di la med //
NK048(tshi)001:157: chu zla zla ba min no zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:158: gnam zlas stong dang chu zla rang //
NK048(tshi)001:159: snang de zung 'jug yin na ko //
NK048(tshi)001:160: zung 'jug rtogs pa sus kyang bla //
NK048(tshi)001:161: ba lang rta min kun gyis shes //
NK048(tshi)001:162: ba lang snang bar mngon sum mthong //
NK048(tshi)001:163: de rtogs ngo mtshar che'o zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:164: bdag nyid chen po ji ste gsungs //
NK048(tshi)001:165: des na rang gi lugs la ni //
NK048(tshi)001:166: chu zla brtags na chu zla nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:167: cung zad mi rnyed med bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:168: chu zla snang bar mngon sum tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:169: med dgag yin kyang snang rung ba //
NK048(tshi)001:170: stong dang yod pa so skye'i blor //
NK048(tshi)001:173: ngo mtshar tshig gis mkhas rnams basngagasa //
NK048(tshi)001:174: stong pa'i ngos nas gzhal ba na //
NK048(tshi)001:175: mi stong cung zad yod min phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:176: med ces mtha' gcig smrar gtub kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:177: med de'i med tshugs ma shor bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:178: snang ba 'gag med nyid du shar //
NK048(tshi)001:179: snang de'i snang tshugs ma shor bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:180: gzhi med stong pa chen por gnas //
NK048(tshi)001:183: nam yang rnyed pa med pa la //
NK048(tshi)001:184: kho thag nang nas chod pa'i tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:185: don tshol mkhan po don med pas //
NK048(tshi)001:186: yid chad skye ba med kyi rting //
NK048(tshi)001:187: yid bde thob pa ngo mtshar che //
NK048(tshi)001:188: 'ga' zhig nyan rang dgra bcom pas //
NK048(tshi)001:189: chos kyi bdag med ma rtogs zer //
NK048(tshi)001:190: phung por nga tsam 'dzin pa'i bdag /
NK048(tshi)001:191: ma kheg de srid de'i nus pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:192: nyon mongs spong ba med pa dang //
NK048(tshi)001:193: bdag de'ang phung po la brten nas //
NK048(tshi)001:194: brtags tsam ngar 'dzin lhan skyes kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:195: yul yin de dang bum sogs la //
NK048(tshi)001:196: stong gzhi'i dbye ba ma gtogs pa //
NK048(tshi)001:197: stong tshul khyad par 'ga' med de //
NK048(tshi)001:198: chos dang gang zag so sor yang //
NK048(tshi)001:199: rang bzhin grub pas stong phyir ro //
NK048(tshi)001:200: de ltar lung dang rigs pas kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:201: mngon sum grub las brgal nas su //
NK048(tshi)001:202: nyan rang chos bdag ma rtogs zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:203: smra ba dam bca' tsam du zad //
NK048(tshi)001:204: de la kha cig thal ches nas //
NK048(tshi)001:205: theg gsum mthong lam gcig pa dang //
NK048(tshi)001:206: rtogs pa mtho dman med par 'dod //
NK048(tshi)001:207: sher phyin sngags sogs mdo rgyud gzhung //
NK048(tshi)001:208: kun kyang drang ba'i don du 'grel //
NK048(tshi)001:209: de la dman lam sngon song ba'i //
NK048(tshi)001:210: theg chen mthong lam thob sogs tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:211: spang bya cung zad med sogs skyon //
NK048(tshi)001:212: rigs pas gnod pa zlog med 'bab //
NK048(tshi)001:213: gzhan yang rtogs bya rtogs gyur kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:214: spang bya spong bar grogs dgos zer //
NK048(tshi)001:215: ma rtogs rtogs par khas blang 'gal //
NK048(tshi)001:216: rtogs na spang bya mi spong 'gal //
NK048(tshi)001:217: nyi ma shar yang mun pa'i dpung //
NK048(tshi)001:218: 'joms pa gzhan la ltos pa mtshar //
NK048(tshi)001:219: kha cig nyan rang rang rgyud kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:220: phung po lnga po stong rtogs kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:221: chos gzhan bdag med mi rtogs zer //
NK048(tshi)001:222: phung po lnga po stong rtogs na //
NK048(tshi)001:223: 'dus ma byas tsam ma gtogs pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:224: ma rtogs dngos gzhan ci zhig yod //
NK048(tshi)001:225: des na rang lugs gang yin na //
NK048(tshi)001:226: dpal ldan zla ba'i rang 'grel las //
NK048(tshi)001:227: nyon mongs spangs phyir nyan rang la //
NK048(tshi)001:228: rgyal bas gang zag bdag med dang //
NK048(tshi)001:229: shes sgrib spangs phyir rgyal sras la //
NK048(tshi)001:230: chos bdag med pa rdzogs par bstan //
NK048(tshi)001:231: 'o na nyan rang gnyis po la //
NK048(tshi)001:232: stong nyid rtogs pa yod do zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:233: smras pa ji ltar yin zhe na //
NK048(tshi)001:234: nyan rang de dag kun nyon tsam //
NK048(tshi)001:235: spangs phyir gang zag med sgom gyi //
NK048(tshi)001:236: chos kyi bdag med rdzogs par ni //
NK048(tshi)001:237: sgom pa med ces gsungs ba bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:238: klong chen rab 'byams zhal snga nas //
NK048(tshi)001:239: sngon gyi slob dpon thams cad ni //
NK048(tshi)001:240: yod dang med ces rtsod na yang //
NK048(tshi)001:241: rang bzhed sngon gyi nyan rang la //
NK048(tshi)001:242: ci rigs snang yang dgra bcom pa //
NK048(tshi)001:244: stong par ma rtogs thar min pas //
NK048(tshi)001:245: de tsam rtogs pa yod na yang //
NK048(tshi)001:246: bdag med rdzogs par rtogs pa med //
NK048(tshi)001:247: yungs 'bru srin gyis zos pa yi //
NK048(tshi)001:248: nang gi mkha' bzhin nyan rang gi /
NK048(tshi)001:249: bdag med chung ngur gsung pa ste //
NK048(tshi)001:250: de phyir dman la dgag pa'i sgras //
NK048(tshi)001:251: chos bdag ma rtogs ces bzhed gsung //
NK048(tshi)001:252: 'di ni phul byung legs bshad de //
NK048(tshi)001:253: 'di dang mtshungs pa gzhan ma mchis //
NK048(tshi)001:254: dper na rgya mtsho chen po'i chu //
NK048(tshi)001:255: hub gang btung yang rgya mtsho de //
NK048(tshi)001:256: ma btung zhes su mi rung ltar //
NK048(tshi)001:257: chos kyi bye brag nga tsam po //
NK048(tshi)001:258: bdag med mthong phyir stong mthong 'dod //
NK048(tshi)001:259: hub gcig 'thung bas rgya mtsho'i chu //
NK048(tshi)001:260: rdzogs par khong du ma song ltar //
NK048(tshi)001:261: mtha' dag shes bya'i rang bzhin kun //
NK048(tshi)001:262: stong par rtogs pa med pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:263: bdag med rdzogs par ma mthong 'dod //
NK048(tshi)001:264: gal te chos gcig stong mthong na //
NK048(tshi)001:265: thams cad mi mthong ci zhe na //
NK048(tshi)001:266: de gas lung rigs man ngag gis //
NK048(tshi)001:267: brtags na de ltar mthong mod kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:268: re zhig nyan thos rigs can rnams //
NK048(tshi)001:269: gang zag med tsam kho na la //
NK048(tshi)001:270: zhen pas mtha' gzhan rtogs dka' ste //
NK048(tshi)001:271: bum pa brtags par 'dod rnams kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:272: rdul phran rdzas su 'dod pa bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:273: gal te bum pa btags par ni //
NK048(tshi)001:274: rtogs pa'i blo des rdul la yang //
NK048(tshi)001:275: dpyad na rtogs par rigs mod kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:276: re zhig ma rtogs de bzhin no //
NK048(tshi)001:277: rag pa'i gzhi dang cha med rdul //
NK048(tshi)001:278: 'gal bar snang yang de dag la //
NK048(tshi)001:279: re zhig lung dang man ngag gis //
NK048(tshi)001:280: dben phyir mi 'gal grub mtha' sgrub //
NK048(tshi)001:281: de bzhin sems tsam dag gis kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:282: gzung ba med na 'dzin pa yang //
NK048(tshi)001:283: ci phyir mi rtogs rang rgyud pas //
NK048(tshi)001:284: don dam bden med rig pa des //
NK048(tshi)001:285: tha snyad du yang rang mtshan gyis //
NK048(tshi)001:286: grub pa med par cis ma rtogs //
NK048(tshi)001:287: des na thams cad thal 'gyur ba //
NK048(tshi)001:288: 'ba' zhig nyid du khyod la thal //
NK048(tshi)001:289: nyan rang theg pa chen po la //
NK048(tshi)001:290: skur zhing smod pa'ang ga la srid //
NK048(tshi)001:291: des na gcig gi rang bzhin nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:292: kun la mnyam nyid yin na yang //
NK048(tshi)001:293: phyi dang nang gi rkyen gyi tshogs //
NK048(tshi)001:294: ma tshangs de srid rtogs pa bul //
NK048(tshi)001:295: spyir na dbang rnon rang stobs kyis //
NK048(tshi)001:296: rtogs pa yod kyi rtul po yis //
NK048(tshi)001:297: rang gi de ma thag tu yang //
NK048(tshi)001:298: nges par rtogs pa'i khyab pa med //
NK048(tshi)001:299: nam zhig cis kyang rtogs nges te //
NK048(tshi)001:300: bskal pa stong phrag bcu yi mthar //
NK048(tshi)001:301: 'gog pa'i dbyings las dgra bcom pa //
NK048(tshi)001:302: ldang ste theg chen 'jug par gsungs //
NK048(tshi)001:303: tshul bzhin theg chen zhugs pas kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:304: grangs med bskal par goms dgos na //
NK048(tshi)001:305: nyan thos zhi bde don gnyer bas //
NK048(tshi)001:306: bskal pa stong phrag de tsam la //
NK048(tshi)001:307: bdag med mtha' dag ma rtogs pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:308: gnas skabs mi srid ci la 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:309: sa thob rnams la'ang chos kyi dbyings //
NK048(tshi)001:310: je bas je gsal rdzogs min nam //
NK048(tshi)001:311: tshogs bsag grogs dang rig pa'i sgo //
NK048(tshi)001:312: mtha' yas tshul dang byang sems kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:313: spyod pa yongs bsngo'i rkyen tshang na //
NK048(tshi)001:314: nges par rdzogs par rtogs 'gyur te //
NK048(tshi)001:315: thabs la mkhas pa'i rkyen tshang bas //
NK048(tshi)001:316: sngags kyi myur du rtogs ba bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:317: rtag bdag spangs kyang lhan skyes kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:319: de phyir phung por 'dzin yod pa //
NK048(tshi)001:320: de srid ngar 'dzin yod gsung don //
NK048(tshi)001:321: gdags bzhi phung po yod gyur cing //
NK048(tshi)001:322: der 'dzin sems pa yod ji srid //
NK048(tshi)001:323: bdag tu gdags pa'i rgyu tshang bas //
NK048(tshi)001:325: gang phyir rtag bdag spangs kyang ni //
NK048(tshi)001:326: gdags gzhir brten nas btags pa'i bdag /
NK048(tshi)001:327: lhan skyes zhen yul ma bkag phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:328: ngar 'dzin skye la gegs med nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:329: de phyir nyon mongs spang ba la //
NK048(tshi)001:330: phung sogs stong par rtogs dgos zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:333: btags pa'i nga tsam shes gyur na //
NK048(tshi)001:334: ngar 'dzin ldog la des chog ste //
NK048(tshi)001:335: thag pa med par ma shes kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:336: sbrul 'dzin sbrul med mthong bas ldog /
NK048(tshi)001:337: mthar ni nges par rtogs dgos te //
NK048(tshi)001:338: chos kun de nyid gcig yin cing //
NK048(tshi)001:339: de nyid mthong ba'i tshul gcig pas //
NK048(tshi)001:340: mthar thug theg gcig 'grub pa yi //
NK048(tshi)001:341: rigs pa klu sgrub yab sras smra //
NK048(tshi)001:342: gal te khyod kyi lugs ltar na //
NK048(tshi)001:343: de nyid nyan rang mthong zin pas //
NK048(tshi)001:344: rigs pa de yis theg gcig tu //
NK048(tshi)001:345: ci zhig 'grub ste dam bca' tsam //
NK048(tshi)001:347: mthar thug gzigs pa de kho na //
NK048(tshi)001:348: de bzhin nyid gcig de yin te //
NK048(tshi)001:350: des na tshul 'di legs rtogs na //
NK048(tshi)001:351: klu sgrub lugs dang byams pa 'i gzhung //
NK048(tshi)001:352: phan tshun bu ra ma sbrang rtsi bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:353: lhan cig yi gas bder 'ju yi //
NK048(tshi)001:354: gzhan du mi 'phrod zas bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:355: khong na mi bde'i skran gyur tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:356: lung rigs gtsags bu rnon po brgya //
NK048(tshi)001:357: gdengs shing 'debs la yid gting sdar //
NK048(tshi)001:358: lta ba'i dngos gzhi skyong ba'i dus //
NK048(tshi)001:359: kha cig cir yang mi 'dzin zer //
NK048(tshi)001:360: cir yang mi 'dzin zhes ba'i don //
NK048(tshi)001:361: legs par rtogs dang log rtog gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:362: dang po mtha' bzhi'i spros bral te //
NK048(tshi)001:363: 'phags pa'i ye shes kyi mdun na //
NK048(tshi)001:364: gang yang gnas pa med mthong bas //
NK048(tshi)001:365: 'dzin stangs ngang gis zhig pa ste //
NK048(tshi)001:366: stong gsal mkha' la lta dang mtshungs //
NK048(tshi)001:367: gnyis pa dran med ha shang lugs //
NK048(tshi)001:368: ma dpyad tse ner bzhag pa yis //
NK048(tshi)001:369: lhag mthong gsal ba'i cha med par //
NK048(tshi)001:370: mtsho gting rdo bzhin tha mal gnas //
NK048(tshi)001:371: dper na ci yang med ces pa //
NK048(tshi)001:372: dbu mas med par mthong ba dang //
NK048(tshi)001:373: gzugs med med par mos pa ltar //
NK048(tshi)001:374: tshig tsam mtshungs pa 'di dag kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:375: don la mi mtshungs gnam sa bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:376: de ltar mtha' bzhi spros bral la //
NK048(tshi)001:377: mtha' bzhi gang du'ang mi 'dzin na //
NK048(tshi)001:380: gal te 'dzin stangs med ces pas //
NK048(tshi)001:381: blun po kha cig dang po nas //
NK048(tshi)001:382: cir mi 'dzin par lhod do lo //
NK048(tshi)001:383: 'gro kun tha mal klod ches pas //
NK048(tshi)001:385: da dung bklags te bskul mi dgos //
NK048(tshi)001:386: gal te de dag mi shes bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:387: bdag cag rang ngo shes zer na //
NK048(tshi)001:388: don dam rang ngo shes pa la //
NK048(tshi)001:389: bden stong phu thag chod pa dgos //
NK048(tshi)001:390: 'khrul snang bdag dang gzhan no zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:391: sus kyang shes la sgom ci dgos //
NK048(tshi)001:392: gal te sems la mdog dbyibs dang //
NK048(tshi)001:393: byung gnas 'gro sa brtag pa'i tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:394: ma mthong stong bar rtogs she na //
NK048(tshi)001:395: chos tshul shin tu zab pa ste //
NK048(tshi)001:396: 'di la'ang gol sa shin tu che //
NK048(tshi)001:397: sems ni gzugs can ma yin pas //
NK048(tshi)001:398: sus kyang mdog sogs mthong mi srid //
NK048(tshi)001:399: ma mthong tsam la stong pa nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:400: ngo 'phrod snyam na shin tu gol //
NK048(tshi)001:401: lan brgyar brtag kyang mi yi mgor //
NK048(tshi)001:402: phyugs kyi r+aa co mthong mi srid //
NK048(tshi)001:403: de ma mthong bas de stong par //
NK048(tshi)001:404: rtogs so zhe na sus kyang sla //
NK048(tshi)001:405: des na rigs pa'i dpyad pa des //
NK048(tshi)001:406: gnas lugs thig po zhig mthong na //
NK048(tshi)001:407: sems de sgyu ma lta bu la //
NK048(tshi)001:408: ngo bo bden med gting nas rig /
NK048(tshi)001:409: de tshe thad ka'i nam mkha' la //
NK048(tshi)001:410: bltas pa bzhin du rang gi sems //
NK048(tshi)001:411: 'gyu bzhin pa yang stong pa yi //
NK048(tshi)001:412: nges shes kho thag chod pa dgos //
NK048(tshi)001:413: yang ni khyod kyi sems de ni //
NK048(tshi)001:415: sna tshogs shes pa gang yin zer //
NK048(tshi)001:416: skad cig mi sdod g.yo ba'i sems //
NK048(tshi)001:417: su la'ang yod phyir shes pa zhig /
NK048(tshi)001:418: 'dug par sus kyang nges par smra //
NK048(tshi)001:419: de nas yod pa ma yin la //
NK048(tshi)001:420: med pa'ang min pa'i sems de ni //
NK048(tshi)001:421: 'od gsal chos sku yin no zer //
NK048(tshi)001:422: des kyang ngo 'phrod rlom pa bcas //
NK048(tshi)001:423: thos pa mang po ma byas kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:424: gcig shes kun grol shes so lo //
NK048(tshi)001:425: rdzogs chen yod min med min ni //
NK048(tshi)001:426: mtha' bzhi'i spros dang bral ba yin //
NK048(tshi)001:427: khyod kyi 'di ni legs brtags na //
NK048(tshi)001:428: yod par smra ru mi btub cing //
NK048(tshi)001:429: med par yang ni smrar med pa //
NK048(tshi)001:430: don du yod med gnyis yin nam //
NK048(tshi)001:431: yang na gnyis ka min pa'i mu //
NK048(tshi)001:432: gang rung zhig las ma 'das par //
NK048(tshi)001:433: sems de yod min med min gyi //
NK048(tshi)001:434: gzhi ru zhe la brnag kyin gda' //
NK048(tshi)001:435: de ni bsam mi khyab pa'i bdag /
NK048(tshi)001:436: de dang ming gi rnam grangs las //
NK048(tshi)001:437: don la 'dod tshul khyad par med //
NK048(tshi)001:438: sems dang de las gzhan gyi chos //
NK048(tshi)001:439: kun kyang bden med nges pa'i steng //
NK048(tshi)001:440: snang ba rten 'byung du shar bas //
NK048(tshi)001:441: yin min bsam brjod las 'das pa //
NK048(tshi)001:442: mtha' bzhi'i spros dang bral ba'i gnad //
NK048(tshi)001:443: gtad med zang ma thal byung ngo //
NK048(tshi)001:444: 'di ni yin min gnyis bral zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:445: blo yi mdun na 'bem bzhin gnas //
NK048(tshi)001:447: srid pa'i chu bo brgyud mar 'jug /
NK048(tshi)001:448: 'di dag zlog pa'i gnyen po ni //
NK048(tshi)001:449: bdag med pa yi 'dzin stangs yin //
NK048(tshi)001:450: de yang med tshul ma shes par //
NK048(tshi)001:451: med par mos pas mi phan te //
NK048(tshi)001:452: thag khrar sbrul du 'khrul pa la //
NK048(tshi)001:453: sbrul med snyam bas mi phan kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:454: med tshul mthong na spangs pa bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:455: de phyir dpyad pas rtogs byas nas //
NK048(tshi)001:456: dpyad tsam nyid du mi bzhag par //
NK048(tshi)001:457: thog med dngos zhen goms ches pas //
NK048(tshi)001:458: yang yang 'dzin stangs bcas te bsgom //
NK048(tshi)001:459: bdag med goms pas bdag lta ba //
NK048(tshi)001:461: don gzigs du mas nan tan bsgrubs //
NK048(tshi)001:462: dang po'i las can 'jug pa'i sgo //
NK048(tshi)001:464: dang po nas de spong zhes pa //
NK048(tshi)001:465: bdud kyi gsang tshig bkye ba yin //
NK048(tshi)001:466: 'dzin stangs des drangs bden stong la //
NK048(tshi)001:467: nges shes mchog tu 'drongs ba'i tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:468: da gdod med 'dzin tsam po ni //
NK048(tshi)001:469: gnas lugs mthar thug ma yin pas //
NK048(tshi)001:470: sgro 'dogs so gnyis bral ba yi //
NK048(tshi)001:471: spros bral stong pa chen po bsgom //
NK048(tshi)001:472: bden stong phu thag chod gyur nas //
NK048(tshi)001:473: stong pa rten 'byung shar ba yi //
NK048(tshi)001:474: snang stong cir yang mi 'dzin la //
NK048(tshi)001:475: me yi kha nas dag pa'i gser //
NK048(tshi)001:476: ji bzhin yid ches rung mod kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:477: gzhan du ches cher zab pa'i gnad //
NK048(tshi)001:478: 'phags bod mkhas grub che rnams kyis //
NK048(tshi)001:479: yun ring 'bad de rtogs pa'i don //
NK048(tshi)001:480: kye ma blun pos yud tsam la //
NK048(tshi)001:481: rtogs par smra la the tshom g.yo //
NK048(tshi)001:483: yod med las 'das don gyi gshis //
NK048(tshi)001:484: yod med cir yang ma grub na //
NK048(tshi)001:485: phyogs rer 'dzin pa spros dang bcas //
NK048(tshi)001:486: de phyir rigs pas rnam dpyad tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:487: cir yang grub pa ma mthong bas //
NK048(tshi)001:488: cir yang 'dzin pa ga la skye //
NK048(tshi)001:489: 'on kyang mtha' bzhi'i spros bral tshul //
NK048(tshi)001:490: dpyad pas drangs pa'i nges shes las //
NK048(tshi)001:491: rang byung 'od gsal shes rab kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:492: lhag mthong mar me bzhin du gsal //
NK048(tshi)001:493: de dang rnam pa 'gal ba yi //
NK048(tshi)001:494: mtha' bzhi'i blo ngan mun pa'i smag /
NK048(tshi)001:496: nam bsgom nges shes skye ba dgos //
NK048(tshi)001:497: mtha' bzhi'i spros pa cig car du //
NK048(tshi)001:498: kheg pa blo 'das gnyug ma'i dbyings //
NK048(tshi)001:499: so so'i skye bo'i sa nyid na //
NK048(tshi)001:500: car phog tshul gyis mthong dka' bas //
NK048(tshi)001:501: mtha' bzhi'i spros pa res 'jog tu //
NK048(tshi)001:502: 'gog pa thos bsam lta ba'i lugs //
NK048(tshi)001:503: de la ji tsam goms pa bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:504: nges shes je bas je gsal nas //
NK048(tshi)001:505: phyin log sgro 'dogs bsnub byas pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:506: blo gros yar zla lta bur 'phel //
NK048(tshi)001:507: cir yang mi 'dzin lta ngan la //
NK048(tshi)001:508: dngos po cir yang ma grub pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:509: nges shes skye ba ga la yod //
NK048(tshi)001:510: des na sgrib pa spong mi nus //
NK048(tshi)001:511: de phyir 'di gnyis khyad par yang //
NK048(tshi)001:512: du ba'i rtags las me bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:513: spang rtogs bog skyed tshul las shes //
NK048(tshi)001:514: gang phyir blun bsgom tha mal pa //
NK048(tshi)001:515: spangs dang rtogs pa'i rgyu min la //
NK048(tshi)001:516: yon tan skye ba'i gegs yin phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:517: rgya ja tshags la drangs pa bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:519: khyad par rgyu 'bras yid ches chung //
NK048(tshi)001:520: yang dag lta ba'i mig ldan na //
NK048(tshi)001:521: sngar med lung dang nyams rtogs 'bar //
NK048(tshi)001:522: stong mthong de yi yon tan las //
NK048(tshi)001:524: yid ches nyon mongs chung bar 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:525: dpyad pas nges shes drangs ba'i ngang //
NK048(tshi)001:526: rtse gcig bzhag pa'i ting 'dzin la //
NK048(tshi)001:527: ma mthong mthong ba dam pa'i don //
NK048(tshi)001:528: mthong don phyogs su ma lhung bas //
NK048(tshi)001:529: cir yang bzung ba med mod kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:530: lkugs pas bu ram myong ba ltar //
NK048(tshi)001:531: yid ches goms pa'i rnal 'byor la //
NK048(tshi)001:532: skye yi dpyad pa kho na min //
NK048(tshi)001:533: theg mchog lta ba bsgom pa la //
NK048(tshi)001:535: la las mi dpyad bzhag ste bsgoms //
NK048(tshi)001:536: dpyad pas don la bsgribs pas na //
NK048(tshi)001:537: ma dpyad sbom por zhog dang zer //
NK048(tshi)001:538: la las dpyad pa kho na byed //
NK048(tshi)001:539: dpyad pa dang bral bsgom pa ni //
NK048(tshi)001:540: gnyid du song ltar mi phan pas //
NK048(tshi)001:541: nam yang dpyad pa dgos so zer //
NK048(tshi)001:542: sgom pa dpyad 'jog mtha' gcig tu //
NK048(tshi)001:543: phyogs rer 'dzin pa mi rung ste //
NK048(tshi)001:544: ma dpyad pa yi 'jog sgom phal //
NK048(tshi)001:545: zhi gnas tsam zhig 'grub srid kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:546: bsgoms pas nges shes mi skye bas //
NK048(tshi)001:547: thar lam mig gcig nges shes nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:548: spangs nas sgrib pa bsal mi nus //
NK048(tshi)001:549: chos kyi rang bzhin ma shes na //
NK048(tshi)001:550: ci zhig bsgoms te tha mal gyi //
NK048(tshi)001:551: rnam rtog bsgoms pas ci la phan //
NK048(tshi)001:552: mig med lam du zhugs pa bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:553: thog med 'khrul pa'i bag chags kyis //
NK048(tshi)001:554: rang bzhin log par zhen gyur pa //
NK048(tshi)001:555: thabs tshul rigs pa brgya dag gis //
NK048(tshi)001:556: 'bad de ma brtag rtogs par dka' //
NK048(tshi)001:557: gang phyir 'khrul snang zhen pa dang //
NK048(tshi)001:558: yang dag don mthong 'gal bas na //
NK048(tshi)001:559: ches goms srid pa'i smag rum 'dir //
NK048(tshi)001:560: de nyid snang ba rnyed par dka' //
NK048(tshi)001:561: sngon nas sbyangs ba'i las kyi 'phro //
NK048(tshi)001:562: smin dang bla ma'i byin rlabs las //
NK048(tshi)001:564: bden stong nges pa srid mod kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:566: kun gyis de ltar rtogs mi nus //
NK048(tshi)001:567: ka dag gdar sha chod pa la //
NK048(tshi)001:568: thal 'gyur lta ba mthar phyin dgos //
NK048(tshi)001:569: spros bral tsam gyi cha nas ni //
NK048(tshi)001:570: de gnyis khyad par med do gsung //
NK048(tshi)001:571: stong par zhen pa bzlog phyir du //
NK048(tshi)001:572: sngags las bde ba chen po bstan //
NK048(tshi)001:573: bde stong gnyis su med pa'i dbyings //
NK048(tshi)001:574: yul dang yul can bral ba yi //
NK048(tshi)001:575: tshul gyis nyams su myong bar byed //
NK048(tshi)001:576: snang dang gsal dang rig pa gsum //
NK048(tshi)001:577: bde ba de yi rnam grangs yin //
NK048(tshi)001:578: snang cha gzugs kyi sku 'dis ni //
NK048(tshi)001:579: srid pa ji srid phan bde yis //
NK048(tshi)001:580: 'gro kun skyobs par mdzad pas na //
NK048(tshi)001:581: mthar thug snying rje'i rang bzhin nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:582: de phyir rang bzhin nyid kyis kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:583: srid zhir mi gnas ye shes che //
NK048(tshi)001:584: gzhi la ji ltar bzhugs pa ltar //
NK048(tshi)001:585: bde stong lam gyi e wam gyis //
NK048(tshi)001:586: bsgrubs pas tshe 'di nyid la yang //
NK048(tshi)001:588: gzhi lam 'bras gsum don du na //
NK048(tshi)001:589: mi phyed rdo rje'i theg pa yi //
NK048(tshi)001:590: 'bras bu bzhi pa'i dbang gi lam //
NK048(tshi)001:591: rig stong rang byung ye shes nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:592: kho na rtsal du bton gyur pa //
NK048(tshi)001:593: 'od gsal rdo rje rtse mo'i lugs //
NK048(tshi)001:594: mthar thug theg pa'i skyel so yin //
NK048(tshi)001:595: ji srid nges shes ma skyes par //
NK048(tshi)001:596: thabs dang dpyad pas nges shes drang //
NK048(tshi)001:597: nges shes skyes na de'i ngang du //
NK048(tshi)001:598: nges shes nyid dang ma bral bsgoms //
NK048(tshi)001:599: nges shes mar me lta bu'i rgyun //
NK048(tshi)001:600: yang dag min rtog snub byed pa //
NK048(tshi)001:601: de la rtag tu nan tan bya //
NK048(tshi)001:602: bral na slar yang dpyad pas drangs //
NK048(tshi)001:603: dang por dpyad pa gal che ste //
NK048(tshi)001:604: dpyad pa bzang pos ma drangs na //
NK048(tshi)001:605: nges shes bzang po ga la skye //
NK048(tshi)001:606: nges shes bzang po ma skyes na //
NK048(tshi)001:607: sgro 'dogs ngan pa ga la nub //
NK048(tshi)001:608: sgro 'dogs ngan pa ma nub na //
NK048(tshi)001:609: las rlung ngan pa ga la 'gag /
NK048(tshi)001:610: las rlung ngan pa ma 'gag na //
NK048(tshi)001:611: 'khor ba ngan pa ga la spong //
NK048(tshi)001:612: 'khor ba ngan pa ma spang na //
NK048(tshi)001:613: sdug bsngal ngan pa ci la 'dzad //
NK048(tshi)001:615: don du bzang ngan yod ma yin //
NK048(tshi)001:616: bzang ngan med par mnyam nyid du //
NK048(tshi)001:617: rtogs pa nges shes bzang po yin //
NK048(tshi)001:619: spangs nas myang 'das ma bsgrubs pas //
NK048(tshi)001:620: 'gal ba ltar snang tshig gi don //
NK048(tshi)001:621: mi 'gal lam gyi gal mdo ste //
NK048(tshi)001:622: lta spyod man ngag gnad gsang 'di //
NK048(tshi)001:623: dpyad de don gyi ro myongs shig /
NK048(tshi)001:624: bar du dpyad 'jog spel dgos te //
NK048(tshi)001:625: dpyad na nges shes skye 'gyur zhing //
NK048(tshi)001:626: ma dpyad tha mal zhen gyur tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:627: dpyad cing dpyad cing nges shes drangs //
NK048(tshi)001:628: nges shes skyes na de ga'i dang //
NK048(tshi)001:629: ma yengs rtse gcig nyid du bsgoms //
NK048(tshi)001:630: nges shes dang ni sgro 'dogs yid //
NK048(tshi)001:631: phan tshun 'gal ba nyid kyi phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:632: dpyad pas sgro 'dogs sun byung bas //
NK048(tshi)001:633: nges shes gong nas gong du spel //
NK048(tshi)001:634: tha mar dpyad pas ma drangs kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:635: nges shes ngang gis skye ba na //
NK048(tshi)001:636: de ga'i ngang du 'jog pa las //
NK048(tshi)001:637: dpyad pas grub zin bsgrub ci dgos //
NK048(tshi)001:638: thag par sbrul med rtogs pa na //
NK048(tshi)001:639: nges shes de gas sbrul 'dzin ldog /
NK048(tshi)001:640: da rung sbrul ni med do zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:641: yang yang dpyad zer blun min nam //
NK048(tshi)001:642: 'phags lam rtogs pa mngon gyur tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:643: da rung dpyod pas mi bsgoms te //
NK048(tshi)001:644: mngon sum rtogs la rgyu mtshan gyi //
NK048(tshi)001:645: yid dpyod sbyor ba ci zhig dgos //
NK048(tshi)001:646: gal te dpyad pa dang bral tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:647: don mthong rtogs pa mi 'grub na //
NK048(tshi)001:648: 'phags dang rgyal ba'i ye shes dang //
NK048(tshi)001:649: 'jig rten gnod med shes pa yis //
NK048(tshi)001:650: bzung rnams khyod la phyin ci log /
NK048(tshi)001:651: nyid du thal te de dag ni //
NK048(tshi)001:652: rtogs zin yin phyir de dag la //
NK048(tshi)001:653: rang dus dpyad pa med pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:654: mtha' bzhi'i spros dang bral ba yi //
NK048(tshi)001:655: nges shes khyad par can gyi ngor //
NK048(tshi)001:657: dmigs gtad dpyod pa skabs mi thob //
NK048(tshi)001:658: gang tshe dpyod pa'i mtshan 'dzin des //
NK048(tshi)001:659: dar gyi srin bu ji bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:660: rtog pa de yis de bcings nas //
NK048(tshi)001:661: yang dag don ji bzhin mi mthong //
NK048(tshi)001:662: nges shes khyad par can 'dis ni //
NK048(tshi)001:663: yin lugs sgrib pa'i smag bsal tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:664: gnyug ma don gyi 'od gsal ngang //
NK048(tshi)001:665: de nyid ma nor mthong ba gang //
NK048(tshi)001:666: so so rang gi ye shes te //
NK048(tshi)001:667: sems byung shes rab ga la yin //
NK048(tshi)001:669: rnam par 'byed cing der rtog la //
NK048(tshi)001:670: gang phyir yul dang yul can dang //
NK048(tshi)001:671: snang stong re re gang du'ang //
NK048(tshi)001:672: mi dmigs mnyam pa'i ye shes 'di //
NK048(tshi)001:673: sems dang sems las byung ba yi //
NK048(tshi)001:674: mtshan nyid can du gnas ma yin //
NK048(tshi)001:675: de phyir dpyad bas drang ba yi //
NK048(tshi)001:676: nges shes mchog la mnyam bzhag pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:677: shes rab dri ma med pa'i rgyus //
NK048(tshi)001:679: lta ba gtan la phab pa dang //
NK048(tshi)001:680: nges pa'i grub mtha' sgrub byed pa //
NK048(tshi)001:681: shan 'byed so sor rtogs pa yi //
NK048(tshi)001:682: shes rab dri med tshad ma yin //
NK048(tshi)001:683: des drangs pa yi nges shes kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:684: lam nas yin lugs gshis pheb pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:685: mnyam bzhag ye shes gang yin pa //
NK048(tshi)001:686: theg chen lam gyi dngos gzhi de //
NK048(tshi)001:689: theg pa yin la chen po'ang yin //
NK048(tshi)001:690: rgyud sde bzhi yi lugs ltar na //
NK048(tshi)001:691: bla med tshig dbang lam 'di ni //
NK048(tshi)001:692: ye shes mthar thug yin mod kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:693: logs su theg par ma bzhag kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:694: dper na mnyam nyid ye shes sku //
NK048(tshi)001:695: rtsal du bton nas 'chad pa yi //
NK048(tshi)001:696: dpal ldan dus kyi 'khor lo la //
NK048(tshi)001:697: rgyud kyi mthar thug bzhed pa bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:698: bla med rgyud sde'i nang nas kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:699: dbang bzhi'i lam gyi ye shes gang //
NK048(tshi)001:701: rgyud sde kun gyi dgongs pa'i mthil //
NK048(tshi)001:702: lan grangs bcu drug bzhus pa'i gser //
NK048(tshi)001:703: shin tu dag pa de bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:704: theg gzhan grub mthas dpyad pa yis //
NK048(tshi)001:705: je bas je dag 'dir mthar phyin //
NK048(tshi)001:706: de phyir shes rab dri med kyis //
NK048(tshi)001:707: tshad mas 'di don grub pa'i tshul //
NK048(tshi)001:708: rgyud dang dgongs pa 'grel kun dang //
NK048(tshi)001:709: chos bzang rigs pas rnam dpyad la //
NK048(tshi)001:710: bsam na bdud kyi yul las 'das //
NK048(tshi)001:711: mi 'phros shes rab smin par byed //
NK048(tshi)001:712: 'on kyang lta ba'i dngos gzhi ni //
NK048(tshi)001:713: snang stong phyogs rer 'dzin pa sogs //
NK048(tshi)001:714: sems dang sems byung spyod yul du //
NK048(tshi)001:715: 'di don ston par byed pa ni //
NK048(tshi)001:716: brjod min brjod byar byas pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:717: mkhas pa'i dgongs pa nyid dang 'gal //
NK048(tshi)001:718: gang phyir a ti yo ga ni //
NK048(tshi)001:719: snang stong bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:720: ye shes yin slad ma dag pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:721: sems las 'das pa kho na'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:722: 'di la ka dag stong pa'i cha //
NK048(tshi)001:723: gtan 'bebs khregs chod lta ba dang //
NK048(tshi)001:724: lhun grub sku dang ye shes kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:725: rang bzhin gtan la 'bebs pa la //
NK048(tshi)001:726: nang gsal gzhon nu bum pa'i skur //
NK048(tshi)001:727: yid ches 'od gsal thod rgal gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:728: gnyis ka'ang so sor dbyer med de //
NK048(tshi)001:729: ka dag lhun grub zung 'jug gi /
NK048(tshi)001:730: ye shes chen po kho na yin //
NK048(tshi)001:731: rgyud sde gzhan na mi shigs pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:732: ye shes ti la ka zhes pa //
NK048(tshi)001:733: 'di dang ming gi rnam grangs tsam //
NK048(tshi)001:734: 'dir ni shin tu gsal por bstan //
NK048(tshi)001:735: rdzogs chen sems sde'i man ngag rer //
NK048(tshi)001:736: mkhas grub so so'i nyams bzhes pas //
NK048(tshi)001:737: phyag chen lam 'bras zhi byed dang //
NK048(tshi)001:738: zung 'jug dbu ma chen po sogs //
NK048(tshi)001:739: mtshan gyi rnam grangs so sor grags //
NK048(tshi)001:740: don la sems las 'das pa yi //
NK048(tshi)001:741: ye shes yin phyir kun kyang mnyam //
NK048(tshi)001:742: sangs rgyas grub thob dgongs pa ni //
NK048(tshi)001:743: gcig ces mkhas kun mgrin gcig smra //
NK048(tshi)001:744: la las rang lugs rdzogs pa che //
NK048(tshi)001:745: phyag chen sogs las 'phags so zer //
NK048(tshi)001:746: ma rtogs lam gyi tha snyad med //
NK048(tshi)001:747: rtogs na dgongs pa gcig pa la //
NK048(tshi)001:748: rigs pas 'thad pa'i dbye ba med //
NK048(tshi)001:749: de bzhin bla med rgyud kun gyi //
NK048(tshi)001:750: bzhi pa'i dbang gi ye shes kun //
NK048(tshi)001:751: rdzogs pa chen po dbye ba med //
NK048(tshi)001:752: 'on kyang de dag thams cad kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:753: 'byung gnas rdzogs chen rgyud sde la //
NK048(tshi)001:754: sems klong man ngag sdes phye ba'i //
NK048(tshi)001:755: zab rgyas khyad par 'phags pa'i gnad //
NK048(tshi)001:756: man ngag thor bu'i nyams len pa //
NK048(tshi)001:757: gzhan la ma grags mang yod par //
NK048(tshi)001:758: khyad chos yin zhes smra ci dgos //
NK048(tshi)001:759: de la rdzogs chen mthar thug pa //
NK048(tshi)001:761: sangs rgyas ye shes yin na yang //
NK048(tshi)001:762: 'dir ni gnas skabs lam dag tu //
NK048(tshi)001:763: ye shes de dang rjes mthun pa //
NK048(tshi)001:764: dpe dang don gyi zung 'jug rnams //
NK048(tshi)001:765: ri mor bris pa'i zla ba dang //
NK048(tshi)001:766: chu zla nam mkha'i zla ba bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:767: rim pas gcig gis gcig 'dren pas //
NK048(tshi)001:768: rang byung zag med ye shes gang //
NK048(tshi)001:769: rang gi blo nus dang bstun te //
NK048(tshi)001:770: nyams su len pa yod nyid phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:771: dper na 'phags lam ye shes gang //
NK048(tshi)001:772: thob phyir rjes mthun bsgom pa bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:773: chos nyid zung 'jug ye shes che //
NK048(tshi)001:774: mngon sum gtan la pheb pa na //
NK048(tshi)001:775: yid dpyod 'dzin pa'i lta ba kun //
NK048(tshi)001:776: nges par nub nas spros bral mthong //
NK048(tshi)001:777: de phyir skabs shan ma phyed par //
NK048(tshi)001:778: 'dzin stangs yod med phyogs gcig tu //
NK048(tshi)001:779: smra la skyon dang legs cha ste //
NK048(tshi)001:781: 'di ni nges pa'i lung bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:782: rigs pa'i tshul gyis grub pa yin //
NK048(tshi)001:783: bden pa gnyis las gang gtso na //
NK048(tshi)001:784: kha cig don dam gtso cher 'dod //
NK048(tshi)001:785: kun rdzob 'khrul pa'i snang ba zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:786: spang byar rtogs shing don dam pa //
NK048(tshi)001:787: ma 'khrul yin pas don dam der //
NK048(tshi)001:788: lta ba rnam dag yin no zer //
NK048(tshi)001:789: kun rdzob ma 'khrul bden gyur na //
NK048(tshi)001:790: don dam stong par mi rung phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:791: de skad du ni gsungs mod kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:792: kun rdzob spangs pa'i pha rol na //
NK048(tshi)001:793: don dam 'ga' yang mi grub ste //
NK048(tshi)001:794: de gnyis thabs dang thabs byung nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:795: brtag bya'i dngos la ma brten par //
NK048(tshi)001:796: de yi dngos med yod min te //
NK048(tshi)001:797: des na dngos dang dngos med pa //
NK048(tshi)001:798: gnyis ka rten 'brel tsam du mtshungs //
NK048(tshi)001:799: gal te stong par zhen pa des //
NK048(tshi)001:800: snang ba rnam par bcad gyur na //
NK048(tshi)001:801: stong pa rten 'byung du shar ba'i //
NK048(tshi)001:802: klu sgrub lugs bzang rnyog mar byas //
NK048(tshi)001:803: stong mthong de yi lam goms nas //
NK048(tshi)001:804: stong dbyings 'ba' zhig rtogs na ni //
NK048(tshi)001:805: 'phags pa'i mnyam bzhag stong pa nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:806: dngos po'i 'jig rgyur khyod la'ang thal //
NK048(tshi)001:807: de phyir gdod nas stong na yang //
NK048(tshi)001:808: stong snang ris su ma chad pas //
NK048(tshi)001:809: stong pa kho na gtso che zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:810: 'dzin pa mthar thug don mi mkhas //
NK048(tshi)001:811: la las don dam phar bcad nas //
NK048(tshi)001:812: kun rdzob tsam gyi ngos nas ni //
NK048(tshi)001:813: rgyud sde'i lta ba mtho da man byed //
NK048(tshi)001:814: don dam stong pas ma zin pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:815: kun rdzob rang nyid lta ba yi //
NK048(tshi)001:816: mtho dman byed chos su mi 'thad //
NK048(tshi)001:817: don dam gdeng dang mi ldan par //
NK048(tshi)001:818: kun rdzob lha ru bsgom pa tsam //
NK048(tshi)001:819: mos pa tsam yin lta ba min //
NK048(tshi)001:820: mu stegs rig sngags 'ga' zhig kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:821: bzla tshe rang nyid gzhan du mos //
NK048(tshi)001:822: la las kun rdzob gal che ste //
NK048(tshi)001:823: bden gnyis zung du 'jug dgos zer //
NK048(tshi)001:824: yang yang kun rdzob phyogs la basngagasa //
NK048(tshi)001:825: zung 'jug lta ba skyong dus na //
NK048(tshi)001:827: bshad pa bzang po ma yi rjes //
NK048(tshi)001:828: nyams len bu chung sleb ma nus //
NK048(tshi)001:830: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i chos skad la //
NK048(tshi)001:831: rtag dang mi rtag bden gnyis sogs //
NK048(tshi)001:832: rgya chad phyogs lhung bral ba yi //
NK048(tshi)001:833: zung 'jug kho na'i grub mtha' skyong //
NK048(tshi)001:834: kun rdzob dang ni don dam pa //
NK048(tshi)001:835: ya bral re re'i steng du ni //
NK048(tshi)001:836: gzhi lam 'bras bu bzhag mi nus //
NK048(tshi)001:837: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum char du'ang //
NK048(tshi)001:839: kun rdzob spangs pa'i pha rol na //
NK048(tshi)001:840: don dam med la don dam pa //
NK048(tshi)001:841: spangs pa'i kun rdzob gzhan med nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:842: gang snang stong pas khyab pa dang //
NK048(tshi)001:843: gang stong snang bas khyab pa ste //
NK048(tshi)001:844: snang na mi stong mi srid cing //
NK048(tshi)001:845: stong de'ang ma snang mi grub phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:846: dngos dang dngos med gnyis po yang //
NK048(tshi)001:847: stong gzhir byas nas stong dgos phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:848: snang kun btags pa tsam zhig la //
NK048(tshi)001:849: stong pa'ang blo yis btags pa tsam //
NK048(tshi)001:850: rig pas dpyad pas nges shes la //
NK048(tshi)001:851: 'di gnyis thabs dang thabs byung ste //
NK048(tshi)001:852: gcig yod na ni gcig med pa //
NK048(tshi)001:854: de phyir snang dang stong pa dag /
NK048(tshi)001:855: so so'i char ni shes na yang //
NK048(tshi)001:856: don du nam yang dbye ba med //
NK048(tshi)001:857: de phyir zung 'jug ces brjod do //
NK048(tshi)001:858: gnas lugs mthong ba'i nges shes ni //
NK048(tshi)001:859: gang mthar lhung ba med phyir ro //
NK048(tshi)001:860: yang dag dpyod pa'i shes rab ngor //
NK048(tshi)001:861: snang dang stong pa 'di gnyis po //
NK048(tshi)001:862: yod mnyam med mnyam ngo bo gcig /
NK048(tshi)001:863: ldog pa tha dad dbye bar 'dod //
NK048(tshi)001:864: de yang dang po'i las can la //
NK048(tshi)001:865: dgag bya 'gog byed lta bur snang //
NK048(tshi)001:866: de tshe gcig tu 'dres pa med //
NK048(tshi)001:867: nam zhig stong pa'i rang bzhin ni //
NK048(tshi)001:868: snang bar 'char la yid ches thob //
NK048(tshi)001:869: de yang gdod nas stong pa dang //
NK048(tshi)001:870: snang ba 'di dag stong pa yis //
NK048(tshi)001:871: stong bzhin snang la snang bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:872: stong mthong nges shes skye ba nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:873: 'di ni mdo rgyud man ngag gi /
NK048(tshi)001:874: lam zab kun gyi rtsa ba ste //
NK048(tshi)001:875: thos bsam sgro 'dogs chod pa'i don //
NK048(tshi)001:876: yang dag lta ba 'khrul med yin //
NK048(tshi)001:877: gnad de je bas je zab tu //
NK048(tshi)001:878: rtogs pas kun rdzob snang ba yang //
NK048(tshi)001:879: rang mtshan zhen pa rim spong bas //
NK048(tshi)001:880: rgyud sde'i theg rim de ltar snang //
NK048(tshi)001:881: yid kyis mos bsgom tsam zhig dang //
NK048(tshi)001:882: snod bcud lhar snang nges shes kyis //
NK048(tshi)001:883: lta ba gdengs su gyur pa gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:884: mtshungs pa'i go skabs mi srid de //
NK048(tshi)001:885: dbu mas chos rnams bden stong du //
NK048(tshi)001:886: nges pa gang de lta yin la //
NK048(tshi)001:887: bram ze'i nad la sngags 'debs tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:888: nad med mos pa lta min bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:889: don dam gnas lugs rtogs pa yis //
NK048(tshi)001:890: kun rdzob lha ru yid ches kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:891: gzhan du 'khrul pa'i snang tshul la //
NK048(tshi)001:892: gnas nas lha ru ji ltar 'grub //
NK048(tshi)001:894: 'khor ba zhes bya gzhan du med //
NK048(tshi)001:895: de spong lam gyi dbye ba rnams //
NK048(tshi)001:896: don dam kho na'i ngos nas min //
NK048(tshi)001:897: don dam tshul gcig nyid yin phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:898: chos can kun rdzob snang ba'i cha //
NK048(tshi)001:899: don dam gshis su mthong goms kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:900: blo nus la brten bya ba dang //
NK048(tshi)001:901: cha mnyam rnal 'byor bla med bstan //
NK048(tshi)001:902: des na bden gnyis so so yis //
NK048(tshi)001:903: rgyud sde'i mtho dman mi 'byed kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:904: bden gnyis zung du 'jug pa la //
NK048(tshi)001:905: ci tsam yid ches thob pa bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:906: nyams len de yi rjes su 'brang //
NK048(tshi)001:907: de phyir bla med rdo rje'i theg /
NK048(tshi)001:908: tshe gcig grol ba ster ba'i lam //
NK048(tshi)001:909: ma nor ji bzhin nyams len na //
NK048(tshi)001:910: mi gcig 'gro bas tha dad par //
NK048(tshi)001:911: mthong ba'i chu yis dpe bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:912: dag pa'i gzigs pa la brten nas //
NK048(tshi)001:913: snang srid gzhir gzhengs dkyil 'khor du //
NK048(tshi)001:914: su zhig yid mi ches par 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:915: gal te de ltar ma shes nas //
NK048(tshi)001:916: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin ma dag pa //
NK048(tshi)001:917: 'dod bzhin lha ru bsgoms pas kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:918: ngan skyugs bum par dri bzang gis //
NK048(tshi)001:919: byugs pa dang 'drar sems pa des //
NK048(tshi)001:920: kye ma mnyam nyid rdo rje'i theg /
NK048(tshi)001:921: sgom pa ri mo'i mar me bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:922: snang tshul ma dag par snang yang //
NK048(tshi)001:923: de ni 'khrul pas grub pa'i mtha' //
NK048(tshi)001:924: gnas tshul yang dag gzigs pa'i don //
NK048(tshi)001:925: mi phyed rdo rje'i grub mthar smra //
NK048(tshi)001:926: snod bcud dag pa'i rten brten par //
NK048(tshi)001:927: min no snyam du lta bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:928: yin no snyam pa'i sgom pa gang //
NK048(tshi)001:930: lam de lam gyi gzugs brnyan nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:931: sol ba bkrus pas mi dkar bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:932: min kyang yin snyam bcos sgom gyis //
NK048(tshi)001:934: bden stong nges shes med bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:935: mu stegs nyi ma pa rnams kyis //
NK048(tshi)001:936: snang ba spangs pas stong pa sogs //
NK048(tshi)001:937: bsgoms pas nyon mongs spong bar 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:938: bya spyod bla med rgyud sde la //
NK048(tshi)001:939: lta ba'i mtho dman med gyur na //
NK048(tshi)001:940: snang srid dag mnyam rtogs pa yi //
NK048(tshi)001:941: lta ba gdengs su gyur bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:942: bdag dang lha la bzang ngan dang //
NK048(tshi)001:943: gtsang dang mi gtsang so sor ni //
NK048(tshi)001:944: ma mthong bzhin du dbye ba ni //
NK048(tshi)001:945: rang gis rang la gnod par zad //
NK048(tshi)001:946: yang na rgyud sde 'og ma bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:947: blang dor nyid du zhen bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:948: bla med sbyor sgrol sha chang sogs //
NK048(tshi)001:949: blang dor mnyam pa nyid spyod pa //
NK048(tshi)001:950: ma rtogs tho co'i spyod pa zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:951: smad par gyur pa de min nam //
NK048(tshi)001:952: ji ltar ji ltar gnas lugs don //
NK048(tshi)001:953: mthong ba'i nges shes lta bar brjod //
NK048(tshi)001:954: lta bas ji ltar thag bcad pa //
NK048(tshi)001:955: de bzhin sgom dang spyod pas skyong //
NK048(tshi)001:956: theg pa lta ba'i mtho dman gyis //
NK048(tshi)001:957: 'byed phyir dgur ma nges shes na //
NK048(tshi)001:958: nang pa'i grub mtha' dma' shos nas //
NK048(tshi)001:959: mthar phyin rdo rje rtse mo'i bar //
NK048(tshi)001:960: sde tshan dgu yi grangs su ni //
NK048(tshi)001:961: 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan yod phyir te //
NK048(tshi)001:962: theg pa mtho dman mang yod kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:963: gsum sogs dgos pas bzhag bzhin no //
NK048(tshi)001:964: des na nang gi ye shes stobs //
NK048(tshi)001:965: ji lta ji ltar stobs 'phel ba //
NK048(tshi)001:966: de lta de ltar snod bcud rnams //
NK048(tshi)001:967: dag dang ma dag so sor mthong //
NK048(tshi)001:968: de phyir snang stong dbyer med gzhi //
NK048(tshi)001:969: bden gnyis dbyer med tshul gyis rtogs //
NK048(tshi)001:970: lam de ji bzhin goms pa las //
NK048(tshi)001:971: sku gnyis zung 'jug ye shes thob //
NK048(tshi)001:972: chu gcig 'gro ba so so la //
NK048(tshi)001:973: mi gcig dngos por snang ba'i tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:974: la las thun mong blta bya de //
NK048(tshi)001:975: chu yin de mthong yul can rnams //
NK048(tshi)001:976: kun kyang tshad ma yin zhes zer //
NK048(tshi)001:977: chu la rang bzhin 'ga' yod na //
NK048(tshi)001:978: tshad ma tshad min mi srid cing //
NK048(tshi)001:979: so so'i yul snang thun min na //
NK048(tshi)001:980: ka bum mthong ba'i blo bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:981: thun mong blta bya mi srid 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:982: la las rlan gsher tsam yin zer //
NK048(tshi)001:983: thun mong so sor rlan gsher tsam //
NK048(tshi)001:984: ma log yod na rlan gsher la //
NK048(tshi)001:985: mi gcig mthong snang mang byung zhing //
NK048(tshi)001:986: gcig mthong gcig la med pa yi //
NK048(tshi)001:987: chu dang rnag sogs gzhi de gang //
NK048(tshi)001:988: gzhan yang nam mkha' mtha' yas par //
NK048(tshi)001:989: rlan gsher gzhi ru ga la 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:990: rlan gsher chu dang gcig yin na //
NK048(tshi)001:991: rnag sogs nyid du snang mi rung //
NK048(tshi)001:992: chu la sogs las tha dad du //
NK048(tshi)001:993: rlan gsher ci yang dmigs pa min //
NK048(tshi)001:994: mi gcig mthong snang so so la //
NK048(tshi)001:995: thun mong blta bya mi srid cing //
NK048(tshi)001:996: thun mong mthun pa'i dngos po la //
NK048(tshi)001:997: so sor snang ba mi srid phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:998: ltos nas bzhag pa tsam zhig las //
NK048(tshi)001:999: dpyad pa'i gzhi zhig khas len na //
NK048(tshi)001:1000: gnas lugs yin par grub dgos pas //
NK048(tshi)001:1001: gang ltar brtags kyang mi 'thad nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:1002: thun mong blta bya med gyur na //
NK048(tshi)001:1003: sems tsam bzhin du yul med par //
NK048(tshi)001:1004: shes nyid yul du khas len dgos //
NK048(tshi)001:1005: de ni 'thad pa ma yin te //
NK048(tshi)001:1006: yul med bzhin du 'dzin pa yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1007: don la med par 'dra ba la //
NK048(tshi)001:1008: zung 'dzin gnyis po'ang kun rdzob tu //
NK048(tshi)001:1009: snang bar mnyam phyir gang snang ba //
NK048(tshi)001:1010: de la brtags nas gzung 'dzin gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1011: yod med phye ba mi 'thad de //
NK048(tshi)001:1012: yul snang yod kyang rdzun pa ltar //
NK048(tshi)001:1013: 'dzin pa snang yang ma grub phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1014: snang tsam thun mong blta bya ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1015: mthun par snang dang mi snang gzhir //
NK048(tshi)001:1016: yod par grub phyir de med par //
NK048(tshi)001:1017: mi rung zlos gar mthong sogs bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:1018: yod tsam 'di las ma gtogs pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1019: yod pa gzhan nas mi srid pas //
NK048(tshi)001:1020: 'di med na ni snang ba kun //
NK048(tshi)001:1021: mi snang nam mkha' lta bur 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:1022: phyi dang nang gi rkyen gyi ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1023: don dngos ji bzhin mi mthong ba //
NK048(tshi)001:1024: sgyu ma'i sngags kyis shing bu la //
NK048(tshi)001:1025: rta dang glang por snang ba bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:1026: de phyir thun mong blta bya ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1027: 'di zhes nges par bzhag mi rung //
NK048(tshi)001:1028: des na rang gi lugs la ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1029: snang stong ris su ma chad pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1030: gzhi nyid cir yang ma grub pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1031: gang snang kun la mnyam pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1032: dngos gcig sna tshogs par yang snang //
NK048(tshi)001:1033: gang la snang stong rung ba na //
NK048(tshi)001:1034: de la thams cad rung bar 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:1035: gang la snang stong mi rung ba //
NK048(tshi)001:1036: de la thams cad rung mi 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:1037: 'o na tshad ma tshad min gyi //
NK048(tshi)001:1038: rnam dabye'ang 'thad pa med ce na //
NK048(tshi)001:1039: gang snang de nyid gzhan nyid du //
NK048(tshi)001:1040: ma snang de phyir tshul mthong des //
NK048(tshi)001:1041: gzhal bya mi grub ma yin te //
NK048(tshi)001:1042: gang phyir dngos kun rang bzhin gyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1043: rang rang ngo bo la gnas pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1044: gcig dang tha dad byar rung ba'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1045: tshad ma grub pa nyid kyi phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1046: de phyir ltos te tshad ma nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:1047: grub kyi rang dbang chos rnams ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1048: tshad mas grub pa ma yin te //
NK048(tshi)001:1049: grub na gnas lugs nyid du thal //
NK048(tshi)001:1050: chu gcig po yang rang 'dzin gyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1051: tshad mas grub kyang ltos med du //
NK048(tshi)001:1052: rang dbang kho nas grub min te //
NK048(tshi)001:1053: don dam dpyod pas mi grub cing //
NK048(tshi)001:1054: yi dwags ngor yang grub mi 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:1055: rang 'dzin yul la mngon sum dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1056: rjes dpag tshad mas nges pa na //
NK048(tshi)001:1057: de yul 'jug ldog mi bslu'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1058: tshad ma don med ma yin no //
NK048(tshi)001:1059: dper na chu gcig la zhes pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1060: mi yi mthong ba la ltos nas //
NK048(tshi)001:1061: bzhag ste lha la ltos na ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1062: bdud rtsi gcig la blta gzhir 'dzin //
NK048(tshi)001:1063: chu la rnag chu bdud rtsi ru //
NK048(tshi)001:1064: mthong tshe gsum ka tshogs min la //
NK048(tshi)001:1065: de gsum gcig kyang tshad min na //
NK048(tshi)001:1066: de las dngos po gzhan zhig tu //
NK048(tshi)001:1067: mthong ba tshad mas sgrub mi nus //
NK048(tshi)001:1068: mthong don gsum ka med 'gyur bas //
NK048(tshi)001:1069: mi mthong chu 'di chu min na //
NK048(tshi)001:1070: gzhan zhig chu ru mi 'thad pas //
NK048(tshi)001:1071: chu zhes bya ba gtan med 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:1072: de lta'i lugs la'ang tshad ma yi //
NK048(tshi)001:1075: ma bslad dbang po'i yul de nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:1076: tshad ma yin par bsgrub dgos te //
NK048(tshi)001:1077: chu dang smig rgyur chur snang bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:1078: des na gnas skabs yi dwags nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:1079: las kyi sgrib pas chu gtsang ma //
NK048(tshi)001:1080: rnag tu snang yang skyon sol na //
NK048(tshi)001:1081: da gdod chu ru snang ba'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1082: ltos nas mis mthong tshad ma dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1083: gzhan pa rkyen gyis bsgyur ba'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1084: re zhig chu ni tshad mar bsgrubs //
NK048(tshi)001:1085: mthar thug rig pas dpyad pas na //
NK048(tshi)001:1086: de kun bag chags snang ba ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1087: gzhan du chu nyid dag pa yi //
NK048(tshi)001:1088: zhing dang sku yang snang ba'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1089: mi yis mthong ba de kho na //
NK048(tshi)001:1090: mtha' gcig tshad mar rung ma yin //
NK048(tshi)001:1091: des na sgrib rkyen je dag pas //
NK048(tshi)001:1092: mthong ba 'og ma la ltos nas //
NK048(tshi)001:1093: gong ma gong ma tshad ma ru //
NK048(tshi)001:1094: khas blang ba ni 'thad pa nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:1095: mthar thug de kho na nyid ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1096: gcig las med phyir de kho na //
NK048(tshi)001:1097: mthong ba'i tshad ma'ang gcig yin te //
NK048(tshi)001:1098: tshad ma gnyis pa mi srid do //
NK048(tshi)001:1099: gnas lugs bden gcig zung 'jug ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1100: tshad ma rang byung ye shes nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:1101: spang bya ma rig gcig pu las //
NK048(tshi)001:1102: med phyir rig dang ma rig tsam //
NK048(tshi)001:1103: de phyir tshad ma'i tshul 'di yis //
NK048(tshi)001:1104: snang kun rang bzhin lhar sgrub pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1105: snga 'gyur ring lugs kho na ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1106: kun mkhyen rong zom pan+di ta'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1107: legs bshad seng ge'i nga ro yin //
NK048(tshi)001:1108: gzhan na lugs 'di tshul bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:1109: smra ba med pas 'di yi thad //
NK048(tshi)001:1110: gang ltar khas blang 'gal bar mthong //
NK048(tshi)001:1111: de la thun mongs blta bya de //
NK048(tshi)001:1112: snang stong re re mi rung ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1113: gal te stong pa tsam yin na //
NK048(tshi)001:1114: 'gro ba su yang rung la yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1115: mkha' yang bum par snang 'gyur zhing //
NK048(tshi)001:1116: bum pa mkha' ltar snang mi 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:1117: snang ba dang bral stong pa tsam //
NK048(tshi)001:1118: blta byar rung na ci mi snang //
NK048(tshi)001:1119: dngos rnams rtag tu yod pa'am //
NK048(tshi)001:1120: med par thal te rgyu med la //
NK048(tshi)001:1121: ji skad brjod kun 'di la mtshungs //
NK048(tshi)001:1122: stong pa'i gnas skabs yin bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:1123: snang med de gnyis 'gal ba'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1124: ma stong pa zhig yod na ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1125: stong tsam snang gzhir bzhag dang 'gal //
NK048(tshi)001:1126: 'o na khyod kyi gong du ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1127: stong snang mi 'gal ci zhe na //
NK048(tshi)001:1128: 'dir ni mthong don tha snyad pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1129: tshad ma'i rnam bzhag skabs yin pas //
NK048(tshi)001:1130: de'i ngor yod med 'gal ba ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1131: dngos gcig steng gi bden pa gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1132: mi 'gal ye shes yul yin phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1133: gal te stong pa dang bral ba'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1134: snang tsam snang gzhir mi rung ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1135: snang de gang ltar snang ba yin //
NK048(tshi)001:1136: 'di zhes ris su ma chad pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1137: snang ba bsam par mi nus phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1138: snang gzhir 'grub pa ma yin te //
NK048(tshi)001:1139: shes byed tshad mas ma mthong bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:1140: yod ces dam bca' tsam du zad //
NK048(tshi)001:1141: gang snang ris su chad gyur na //
NK048(tshi)001:1142: de las gzhan du snang mi rung //
NK048(tshi)001:1143: mi stong snang ba yin phyir yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1144: de nyid rigs pas dpyad bzod 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:1145: chu rnag bdud rtsi sogs kyi gzhi //
NK048(tshi)001:1146: de gsum gang yin kyang 'gal te //
NK048(tshi)001:1147: gal te chu de rnag yin na //
NK048(tshi)001:1148: chu ru snang ba ji ltar 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:1149: gal te rnag min chu yin na //
NK048(tshi)001:1150: rnag sogs gzhan du ci la snang //
NK048(tshi)001:1151: yi dwags yul du snang de yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1152: chu yin zhe na rnag snang yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1153: med par khas blang nyid du thal //
NK048(tshi)001:1154: gang phyir rang la snang de las //
NK048(tshi)001:1155: snang gzhi logs su yod min te //
NK048(tshi)001:1156: yod na tha dad du 'gyur phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1157: ka bum gcig gzhi gcig min bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:1158: des na snang stong zung 'jug gam //
NK048(tshi)001:1159: bden stong snang ba tsam zhig de //
NK048(tshi)001:1160: rgya chad phyogs lhung bral ba yi //
NK048(tshi)001:1161: zung 'jug ro mnyam chen po ru //
NK048(tshi)001:1162: chos kun gdod nas mnyam pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1163: mnyam nyid rdzogs pa chen po ru //
NK048(tshi)001:1164: grub don gtan la phab byas nas //
NK048(tshi)001:1165: tshul de goms pa'i lam gyi skabs //
NK048(tshi)001:1166: dag pa'i gzigs pa la brten nas //
NK048(tshi)001:1167: ma dag snang ba rang grol ba'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1168: snang srid dag pa'i chos sku zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:1169: yid ches rdo rje'i lung don 'byor //
NK048(tshi)001:1170: nges na sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las //
NK048(tshi)001:1171: phung lnga sgyu ma lta bu yi //
NK048(tshi)001:1172: snang ba ris su ma chad pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1173: de nyid dag pa'i lha snang zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:1174: dgongs pa'i don la yid ches nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:1176: 'khrul bar rtogs shing de goms pas //
NK048(tshi)001:1177: de la chu ru snang ba nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:1178: dag pa'i rgyal sras chen po yis //
NK048(tshi)001:1179: chu yi rdul rer grangs med zhing //
NK048(tshi)001:1180: mthong zhing chu de m+aa ma kir //
NK048(tshi)001:1181: mngon sum snang ba nyid du 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:1182: mthar thug sgrib gnyis spang ba'i sar //
NK048(tshi)001:1183: zung 'jug ro mnyam chen por gzigs //
NK048(tshi)001:1184: de phyir dag pa'i gzigs pa ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1185: sgrib pa ma lus spangs pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1186: dngos po'i gnas tshul ma nor pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1187: de yis mthong ba kho na las //
NK048(tshi)001:1188: gzhan du yod pa ma yin na //
NK048(tshi)001:1189: de nyid mthar thug tshad ma ru //
NK048(tshi)001:1190: bzung ste 'a di kun gdod nas kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:1191: dag pa'i chos skur gnas so zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:1192: dam bca' grub pa'i rtse mo ru //
NK048(tshi)001:1193: rigs pa'i mig ldan rnams la grub //
NK048(tshi)001:1194: de lta na yang theg pa de //
NK048(tshi)001:1195: ngo mtshar 'od zer stong mnga' bas //
NK048(tshi)001:1196: dman pa'i yid can 'byung po'i bya //
NK048(tshi)001:1197: phal cher long ba lta bur gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:1198: de la mthar thug mnyam nyid dbyings //
NK048(tshi)001:1199: lha snang kho nar snang ngo zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:1200: phyogs gcig sgrub par mi nus kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:1201: rang bzhin gdod nas dag pa yi //
NK048(tshi)001:1202: dbyings dang snang cha ye shes sku //
NK048(tshi)001:1204: gdod nas lha ru dag pa la //
NK048(tshi)001:1205: gnas lugs dpyad pas kyang mi gnod //
NK048(tshi)001:1206: gang phyir sgrib gnyis spangs pa yi //
NK048(tshi)001:1207: snang stong zung 'jug dbyings de ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1208: mthar thug de kho na nyid yin //
NK048(tshi)001:1209: de las gzhan du gang ltar du //
NK048(tshi)001:1210: rtogs kyang mthar thug don min te //
NK048(tshi)001:1211: sgrib gnyis zad par ma spangs pas //
NK048(tshi)001:1212: gnas snang rnam kun mi mthun phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1213: gnas skabs lam gyi snang ba la //
NK048(tshi)001:1214: mig skyon dag pa'i rab rib bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:1215: yul can dri mas dag pa las //
NK048(tshi)001:1216: yul kyang de bzhin dag mthong ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1217: yul can dag kyang logs shig na //
NK048(tshi)001:1218: yul de ma dag med pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1219: de lta na yang gang zag gcig /
NK048(tshi)001:1220: 'tshang rgya de tshe ma dag dngos //
NK048(tshi)001:1221: gzhan la mi snang mi 'gyur te //
NK048(tshi)001:1222: rang snang sgrib pas rang bsgribs phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1223: des na yul dang yul can rnams //
NK048(tshi)001:1224: rang bzhin gdod nas dag na yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1225: glo bur dri mas bsgribs pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1226: dri ma sbyang la 'bad par bya //
NK048(tshi)001:1227: sbyang bya'i dri ma rnams kyang ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1228: rang gi ngo bos dag pa las //
NK048(tshi)001:1229: logs shig ma dag pa min pas //
NK048(tshi)001:1230: rang bzhin 'od gsal mnyam pa nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:1231: de ltar snang tshul sna tshogs pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1232: ma rtogs dus na so sor 'dzin //
NK048(tshi)001:1233: byis pa gang la sems chags pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1234: de ni byis pa rmongs pa ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1235: rmongs pa de yis 'ching bar byed //
NK048(tshi)001:1236: rtogs na kun kyang ro mnyam gyi //
NK048(tshi)001:1237: ngang du 'bras bu'i btsan sa zin //
NK048(tshi)001:1238: dus gsum dus med gnyug ma'i klong //
NK048(tshi)001:1239: rang byung ye shes rgyal bar 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:1240: dag mnyam chen po khas len pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1241: tshul 'di legs par grub pa ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1242: snang stong cir yang ma grub pas //
NK048(tshi)001:1243: cir yang rung la cir yang snang //
NK048(tshi)001:1244: de las gzhan du gang btags pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1245: cir yang mi rung cir mi snang //
NK048(tshi)001:1246: tshul 'di'i yid ches rnyed pa'i sgo //
NK048(tshi)001:1247: stong dang rten 'byung lam yin te //
NK048(tshi)001:1248: snang stong 'di la nges shes na //
NK048(tshi)001:1249: bri gang bral ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK048(tshi)001:1250: srid pa stong dang mi stong sogs //
NK048(tshi)001:1251: chos nyid bsam gyis mi khyab la //
NK048(tshi)001:1252: zab mo'i bzod pa khong nas skye //
NK048(tshi)001:1253: rdul gcig khyon la rdul snyed zhing //
NK048(tshi)001:1254: mthong zhing skad cig yun la yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1255: bskal bar snang ste dngos po rnams //
NK048(tshi)001:1256: bden stong sgyu ma'i nges shes kyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1257: sangs rgyas spyod yul nyid la 'jug /
NK048(tshi)001:1258: de phyir rang snang ris med dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1259: rgya chad phyogs lhung bral ba dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1260: gzhi dbyings bsam gyis mi khyab dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1261: chos nyid cir yang ma grub dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1262: snang stong zung du 'jug pa sogs //
NK048(tshi)001:1263: grub mtha'i chos skad tsam 'di'i don //
NK048(tshi)001:1264: lo brgyar bsgrims te bsam byas kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:1265: sngon goms smin pa'i rgyu med na //
NK048(tshi)001:1266: blo chen sbyangs pa mi dman mod //
NK048(tshi)001:1267: thugs su chud pa ma yin no //
NK048(tshi)001:1268: de phyir grub mtha' mtha' dag gi /
NK048(tshi)001:1269: gting phug gang du gzhol ba yi //
NK048(tshi)001:1270: brgya phrag chos kyi legs bshad klung //
NK048(tshi)001:1272: snang tshul gzhan rnams ma nges shing //
NK048(tshi)001:1273: 'gyur ba dag dang bcas te snang //
NK048(tshi)001:1274: mthar phyin zung 'jug ye shes ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1275: bslu med don gzigs 'gyur ba med //
NK048(tshi)001:1276: spros bral dbu ma chen po la //
NK048(tshi)001:1277: khas len yod med dpyad pa'i tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:1278: snga rabs pa rnams mgrin gcig tu //
NK048(tshi)001:1279: dbu ma'i rang lugs yin min dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1280: yod med la sogs cir yang ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1281: med phyir khas len med par 'dod //
NK048(tshi)001:1282: rang gzhung rnams las lam 'bras dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1283: rten 'byung grub mtha'i rnam bzhag kun //
NK048(tshi)001:1284: khas blang rang lugs yod bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:1285: tha snyad thams cad gzhan ngo la //
NK048(tshi)001:1286: skyel ba tshig don gnyis kar 'gal //
NK048(tshi)001:1288: dbu mar khas len yod med la //
NK048(tshi)001:1289: snga rabs pa rnams phyogs rer 'dzin //
NK048(tshi)001:1290: lugs rer skyon yon gnyis re gnas //
NK048(tshi)001:1291: des na rang gis bzhed pa la //
NK048(tshi)001:1292: don dam gnas lugs gzhal ba'i tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:1293: gshis la cir yang ma grub ltar //
NK048(tshi)001:1294: khas kyang ci zhig len par byed //
NK048(tshi)001:1295: de phyir grub mtha' gnas lugs kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:1296: khas len yin phyir rtsod sogs tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:1297: gshis bzhin khas len ci yang med //
NK048(tshi)001:1298: rjes thob lam 'bras grub pa'i mtha' //
NK048(tshi)001:1299: ji ltar ji snyed rnam bzhag rnams //
NK048(tshi)001:1301: phyin chad tshul 'di smra shes na //
NK048(tshi)001:1302: kho bo'i legs bshad mthu yin gsungs //
NK048(tshi)001:1303: der brten gangs can mkhas pa 'gas //
NK048(tshi)001:1304: rang lugs khas len yod pa'i phyogs //
NK048(tshi)001:1305: kho na yang yang ches cher bsgrubs //
NK048(tshi)001:1306: de yang skabs shan ma phyes na //
NK048(tshi)001:1307: gshis don cir yang ma grub phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1308: mtha' gcig khas len yod pa'ang dka' //
NK048(tshi)001:1309: dbu ma rang gi lugs zhes pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1310: dbu ma'i grub mtha' mthar thug don //
NK048(tshi)001:1311: ji ltar gzhal nyid yin dgos te //
NK048(tshi)001:1312: de las gzhan pa rang lugs min //
NK048(tshi)001:1313: ci slad dbu ma rang gis ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1314: gzhal na de ma grub phyir ro //
NK048(tshi)001:1315: des na des khas blangs yin na //
NK048(tshi)001:1316: rang dbang dpyad nas khas blang bar //
NK048(tshi)001:1317: rigs pas 'phul nus nyid kyi phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1318: khas blangs pa de don dam par //
NK048(tshi)001:1319: grub cing dpyad bzod nyid du 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:1320: rang lugs khas len ma yin na //
NK048(tshi)001:1321: rang la khas len yod pa 'gal //
NK048(tshi)001:1322: rang la dpyad dang ma dpyad pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1323: khas len gnyis ni yod gyur cing //
NK048(tshi)001:1324: gnyis ka nges par bden gyur na //
NK048(tshi)001:1325: rang lugs zhes pa de gnyis po //
NK048(tshi)001:1326: re re yin nam gnyis ka yin //
NK048(tshi)001:1327: re re yin na gcig shos 'gal //
NK048(tshi)001:1328: yod pa khas blangs ma yin la //
NK048(tshi)001:1329: med par khas ni blangs gyur na //
NK048(tshi)001:1330: yod ces bya ba'i khas len ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1331: kun rdzob tu yang mi rung ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1332: med pa kho na khas blang phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1333: gnyis kar rang gi khas blangs na //
NK048(tshi)001:1334: dpyad mi bzod pa bsal nas su //
NK048(tshi)001:1335: rigs pas gnod med khas len pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1336: min phyir gnyis ka dpyad bzod 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:1337: de lta na yang de gnyis po //
NK048(tshi)001:1338: tshogs pa srid pa ma yin te //
NK048(tshi)001:1339: tshogs na dpyad pas rtogs na yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1340: ma dpyad dus bzhin yod rtog nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:1341: yod phyir dpyad pas ci zhig phan //
NK048(tshi)001:1342: kun rdzob dpyad grub rigs ma yin //
NK048(tshi)001:1343: dgag bya bcad pa'i med dgag las //
NK048(tshi)001:1344: lhag pa'i gnas lugs med gyur na //
NK048(tshi)001:1345: 'dzin stangs de la snang ba'i cha //
NK048(tshi)001:1346: skabs mi thob phyir mtha' gcig tu //
NK048(tshi)001:1347: lta sgom spyod pa'i skabs kun kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:1348: med par lta ba'i yid can du //
NK048(tshi)001:1349: ci phyir mi 'gyur gnas lugs dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1350: rjes mthun nam yang goms dgos phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1351: des na kun mkhyen bzhed pa bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:1352: rang lugs 'di ltar shes par bya //
NK048(tshi)001:1353: dbu ma mtshan nyid pa yin na //
NK048(tshi)001:1355: spros bral dbu ma yin dgos te //
NK048(tshi)001:1356: 'phags pa'i mnyam bzhag ye shes dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1357: rjes su mthun par gtan phabs nas //
NK048(tshi)001:1358: yod med la sogs mtha' rnams kun //
NK048(tshi)001:1359: nyer zhi'i rang bzhin yin phyir ro //
NK048(tshi)001:1360: stong pa 'ba' zhig yul byed pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1361: lam de bden gnyis phyogs gcig la //
NK048(tshi)001:1362: ltung phyir nyi tshe'i lta ba de //
NK048(tshi)001:1363: zung 'jug dang ni spros bral min //
NK048(tshi)001:1365: snang dang stong pa mnyam nyid kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:1366: 'di ni don dam stong pa'i dbyings //
NK048(tshi)001:1367: 'ba' zhig yul can yin phyir ro //
NK048(tshi)001:1368: spros pa yod med la sogs pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1369: dmigs pa'i rnam pa thams cad de //
NK048(tshi)001:1370: 'di ni med pa'i spros pa dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1371: ma bral de la dmigs pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1372: des na dbu ma chen po'i ngor //
NK048(tshi)001:1373: khas len ci yang yod min te //
NK048(tshi)001:1374: de yis snang stong mnyam nyid du //
NK048(tshi)001:1375: rtogs slad yod med yin min sogs //
NK048(tshi)001:1376: dgag sgrub spros kun bral bas na //
NK048(tshi)001:1377: gnas lugs don bzhin chos kun kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:1378: khas blang rigs pas mi grub phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1379: gang du khas ni len mi byed //
NK048(tshi)001:1380: de ltar gnas lugs mthar thug don //
NK048(tshi)001:1381: khas len med kyang snang tshul la //
NK048(tshi)001:1382: tha snyad bden gnyis so sor yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1383: khas blang yod de de gnyis kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:1384: bden gnyis dbyer med gnas lugs la //
NK048(tshi)001:1385: ltos na so so'i snang tshul tsam //
NK048(tshi)001:1386: dbyer med don mthong ye shes la //
NK048(tshi)001:1387: ltos na tshad ma gnyis po yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1388: nyi tshe'i gnas yin de gcig gis //
NK048(tshi)001:1389: bden gnyis 'dzin pa mi srid phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1390: des na tha snyad don dam gyi //
NK048(tshi)001:1391: tshad ma gnyis po shes rab ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1392: bum sogs de gnyis kyis gzhal na //
NK048(tshi)001:1393: ngo bo gnyis ni rnyed na yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1394: gcig tshe gcig ni yod min pas //
NK048(tshi)001:1395: so skye'i blo la bden pa gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1396: res 'jog tshul las mi snang phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1397: so so gzhal ba'i khas len gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1398: yod pa nyid du grub pa yin //
NK048(tshi)001:1399: 'o na khas len yod med dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1400: bden gnyis khas len nang 'gal tshul //
NK048(tshi)001:1401: gong du gzhan la ji brjod pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1402: rang la'ang mtshungs par thal zhe na //
NK048(tshi)001:1403: nged kyis khyad par phyes nas su //
NK048(tshi)001:1404: shan 'byed lam gyi dbu ma dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1405: dngos gzhi mnyam bzhag dbu ma gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1406: rags dang phra ba'am rgyu 'bras sam //
NK048(tshi)001:1407: rnam shes ye shes gnas skabs kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:1408: dbu ma che chung khyad phyes nas //
NK048(tshi)001:1409: bshad phyir skyon de ga la 'jug /
NK048(tshi)001:1410: des na dbu ma chen po la //
NK048(tshi)001:1411: khas len med pa rang gi lugs //
NK048(tshi)001:1412: mthar thug de yin rjes thob la //
NK048(tshi)001:1413: bden gnyis so sor snang ba'i tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:1414: bden gnyis so so'i tshad ma yis //
NK048(tshi)001:1415: gzhal ba'i dgag sgrub thams cad kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:1416: log rtog re re dgag pa'i ched //
NK048(tshi)001:1417: yin gyi gshis la dgag sgrub tu //
NK048(tshi)001:1418: khas blang gang yang med pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1419: gshis la bden pa gnyis po yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1420: ris su chad pa yod med pas //
NK048(tshi)001:1421: khas len gnyis po gang ltar yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1422: bden par grub pa med pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1423: gnyis kar yang ni khas blangs kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:1424: snang tshul tsam gyi dbang phyir dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1425: gnas skabs gnyis ka so so na //
NK048(tshi)001:1426: bden de 'gal ba med pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1427: dpyad bzod la sogs skyon mi 'bab //
NK048(tshi)001:1428: dngos po'ang dpyad par mi bzod de //
NK048(tshi)001:1429: dngos med kyang ni dpyad mi bzod //
NK048(tshi)001:1430: mthar thug gnyis ka mtshungs pa la //
NK048(tshi)001:1431: gnas skabs ltos te btags pa tsam //
NK048(tshi)001:1432: ma brtags grags pas yod tsam de //
NK048(tshi)001:1433: snang tshul yin gyis gnas tshul min //
NK048(tshi)001:1434: bden med dpyod pa'i rig shes kyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1435: mthong ba gnas tshul don dam 'dod //
NK048(tshi)001:1436: de yang kun rdzob la ltos pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1437: don dam yin gyi mthar thug la //
NK048(tshi)001:1438: ltos na don dam rnam grangs tsam //
NK048(tshi)001:1439: gnas snang phan tshun 'gal ba na //
NK048(tshi)001:1440: bden gnyis tha dad skyon bzhi 'bab //
NK048(tshi)001:1441: gnas snang phan tshun gzhan min na //
NK048(tshi)001:1442: bden gnyis gcig pa'i skyon bzhis gnod //
NK048(tshi)001:1443: tshul des sangs rgyas sems can kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:1444: gnas tshul snang tshul tsam yin gyi //
NK048(tshi)001:1446: theg pa chung ngur shes par bya //
NK048(tshi)001:1447: gnas snang gcig dang tha dad du //
NK048(tshi)001:1448: khas blangs med phyir sems can ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1449: sangs rgyas yin na snang rung dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1450: lam dang sgrub pa don med dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1451: rgyu la 'bras gnas khas len sogs //
NK048(tshi)001:1452: rigs pas gnod pa rnam kun med //
NK048(tshi)001:1453: gnas tshul gang yin sgrib pa yis //
NK048(tshi)001:1454: bsgribs phyir nye bar mi snang bas //
NK048(tshi)001:1455: lam la 'bad par byed pa ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1456: rang gzhan gnyis kas 'dod pa nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:1457: bden gnyis 'gal ba med pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1458: yod dang med ces lta ba yi //
NK048(tshi)001:1459: khas len gnyis po'ang ji ltar 'gal //
NK048(tshi)001:1460: phan tshun gcig pa'ang min pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1461: khas blang gnyis kyi rnam par bzhag /
NK048(tshi)001:1462: de phyir ji srid bden pa gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1463: so sor snang ba dang bcas pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1464: sems kyi 'jug pa yod kyi bar //
NK048(tshi)001:1465: de gnyis rnam kun stobs mtshungs pas //
NK048(tshi)001:1466: mtha' gcig khas len yod min te //
NK048(tshi)001:1467: med ces bden stong nges pa dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1468: yod ces snang cha nges pa gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1469: res 'jog tshad ma gnyis kyis ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1470: gzhal tshe so sos rnyed don nam //
NK048(tshi)001:1471: mthong don bden pa gnyis zhes brjod //
NK048(tshi)001:1472: de gnyis gcig dang tha dad pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1473: min phyir de gnyis mtha' gcig tu //
NK048(tshi)001:1474: gcig spang gcig ni bzung mi rung //
NK048(tshi)001:1475: de gnyis la dpyod shes rab kyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1476: khas len so sor phye ste dper //
NK048(tshi)001:1477: mthar thug chos sku 'thob pa'i tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:1478: sems dang sems byung ma lus pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1479: tha snyad dbang du 'gag ces bya //
NK048(tshi)001:1480: dam pa'i don du 'gag pa'ang med //
NK048(tshi)001:1481: mdo dang bstan bcos gzhung kun na //
NK048(tshi)001:1482: dgag sgrub rnam pa ji snyed pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1483: la la don dam khas len te //
NK048(tshi)001:1484: la la kun rdzob dbang du gsungs //
NK048(tshi)001:1485: don dam kho na'i dbang du na //
NK048(tshi)001:1486: lam dang sangs rgyas sems can sogs //
NK048(tshi)001:1487: med ces smra bar rung mod kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:1488: kun rdzob nyid la ltos med du //
NK048(tshi)001:1489: de gcig kho nar mi 'gyur te //
NK048(tshi)001:1491: snang bar mngon sum grub pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1492: tha snyad tshad ma'i dbang byas nas //
NK048(tshi)001:1493: lam dang sangs rgyas sems can sogs //
