NK048(tshi)001:1494: yod ces brjod par rigs mod kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:1495: don dam nyid la ltos med du //
NK048(tshi)001:1496: de gcig kho nar mi 'gyur te //
NK048(tshi)001:1497: yod kyang de ltar ma grub par //
NK048(tshi)001:1498: dpyad pa tshad mas nges pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1499: des na de gnyis nam du yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1500: gcig med gcig yod srid ma yin //
NK048(tshi)001:1501: gnyis ka stobs mtshungs bden gyur tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:1502: dngos po mi stong 'gyur zhe na //
NK048(tshi)001:1503: gnyis ka'ang rang bzhin ma grub dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1504: yul gnyis don gyis tha dad pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1505: ma yin snang ba de'i ngo bo //
NK048(tshi)001:1506: stong phyir mi stong ga la yin //
NK048(tshi)001:1507: gnyis ka mtshungs bar snang de'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1508: stong par grub ste snang med na //
NK048(tshi)001:1509: stong pa'ang ci yis shes par 'gyur //
NK048(tshi)001:1510: des na gnyis ka mi 'gal bar //
NK048(tshi)001:1512: gcig yod gcig la nges shes na //
NK048(tshi)001:1514: gang la gang gis ma khyab pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1515: med phyir gang ltar gzhal kyang bden //
NK048(tshi)001:1516: snang ba stong par shes pa yis //
NK048(tshi)001:1517: snang ba bden pa med par rtogs //
NK048(tshi)001:1518: stong pa snang bar shes na yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1519: stong pa bden par yod mi rtogs //
NK048(tshi)001:1521: bden par nam yang slar mi ldog /
NK048(tshi)001:1522: gang snang de yi gnas lugs ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1524: snang ba spang ba'i pha rol tu //
NK048(tshi)001:1525: stong pa yan gar mi 'grub phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1526: des na ji srid res 'jog gis //
NK048(tshi)001:1527: bden gnyis bsgom pa shes rab ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1529: sems dang sems byung g.yo ba yis //
NK048(tshi)001:1530: ye shes nye bar mi snang phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1531: dpyad pa'i shes rab dri med gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1532: spang blang med par gzung bya ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1533: gang tshe gcig ma tshang gyur na //
NK048(tshi)001:1534: de gnyis las byung zung 'jug gi /
NK048(tshi)001:1535: ye shes nges par mi skye ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1536: gtsubs shing gtsubs stan gang rung dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1537: bral ba'i me ni 'byung min bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:1538: des na thabs dang stong pa nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:1539: ya bral yang dag lam min zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:1540: rgyal dang brgyud 'dzin gyis gsungs phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1541: rgyu gnyis 'di spang ye shes che //
NK048(tshi)001:1542: skyee ba'i thabs gzhan mi srid de //
NK048(tshi)001:1543: ye shes rang gi ngo bo ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1544: bsam brjod 'das phyir brda' thabs dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1545: tshig tsam dag gis mtshon pa las //
NK048(tshi)001:1546: dngos su bstan par mi nus pas //
NK048(tshi)001:1547: sngags su tshig dbang zhes gsungs te //
NK048(tshi)001:1548: rdo rje snying po'i rgyud sogs su //
NK048(tshi)001:1549: tshig dang thabs kyi sgo nas bstan //
NK048(tshi)001:1551: de ltar gzhan la ma ltos par //
NK048(tshi)001:1552: gzung bar nus pa ma yin pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1553: bden gnyis lam gyi dbu ma bstan //
NK048(tshi)001:1554: bden gnyis tshul gyis dpyad pa'i 'bras //
NK048(tshi)001:1555: zung 'jug nyid du grub nus pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1556: des na bden gnyis gtan 'bebs tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:1557: snang stong dgag bya 'gog byed kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:1558: tshul du res 'jog lta bur bstan //
NK048(tshi)001:1560: rgyud sder rnam grangs du mas bstan //
NK048(tshi)001:1561: des na dbu ma'i lugs thams cad //
NK048(tshi)001:1562: bden gnyis tshul gyis rnam par bzhag /
NK048(tshi)001:1563: bden pa gnyis la ma brten par //
NK048(tshi)001:1565: rgyal bas ji snyed gsungs pa yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1566: bden pa gnyis la yang dag brten //
NK048(tshi)001:1567: de phyir bden gnyis so so yi //
NK048(tshi)001:1568: khas len dang bcas dbu ma de //
NK048(tshi)001:1569: 'bras ming rgyu la btags pa yi //
NK048(tshi)001:1570: res 'jog dbu ma chung ngu yin //
NK048(tshi)001:1571: phung po rnam dpyad stong pa nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:1572: dgag bya bcad pa'i med dgag tsam //
NK048(tshi)001:1573: de la ltos na med ces pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1574: khas len kyang ni yod pa yin //
NK048(tshi)001:1575: rgyu'am lam gyi dbu ma des //
NK048(tshi)001:1576: bden gnyis ji ltar khas blangs pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1577: gnyis ka rang gi lugs yin gyi //
NK048(tshi)001:1578: don dam rang lugs byas nas su //
NK048(tshi)001:1579: kun rdzob gzhan ngor skyel ba min //
NK048(tshi)001:1580: yin na rang lugs don dam pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1581: rkyang rkyang po ru gyur nas kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:1582: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i snang ba kun //
NK048(tshi)001:1583: 'khrul ba spang bya kho na zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:1584: skur pa 'debs shing mthar phyin tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:1585: sgrib bral dbyings stong 'ba' zhig tsam //
NK048(tshi)001:1586: lhag mar lus nas mkhyen gnyis sogs //
NK048(tshi)001:1587: med 'dod nyan rang rang lam gyi //
NK048(tshi)001:1589: 'dir yang mar me rgyun chad dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1590: don khyad med phyir zung 'jug dbyings //
NK048(tshi)001:1591: med par skur 'debs nam mkha' dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1593: bstan pa'i rkun po dam pa'i chos //
NK048(tshi)001:1594: 'jig pa'i skyes bur rgyal bas gsungs //
NK048(tshi)001:1595: rigs pas kyang ni de 'dra'i lugs //
NK048(tshi)001:1596: yod la med par skur ba'i tshul //
NK048(tshi)001:1597: yin par nges shes rdo rje'i mes //
NK048(tshi)001:1598: lta ngan ri bo brlag par nus //
NK048(tshi)001:1599: des na dbu ma'i gzhung kun tu //
NK048(tshi)001:1600: shes rab rgyu yi dbu ma nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:1601: rigs pas dpyad cing ma grub par //
NK048(tshi)001:1603: bden pa gnyis kyi tshul du ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1604: rigs pas gtan la phab na yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1605: 'bras bu bden pa dbyer med du //
NK048(tshi)001:1606: grub pa rgyu 'bras theg pa'i bcud //
NK048(tshi)001:1607: de phyir ye shes de dag ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1608: res 'jog tshul gyis mtha' gnyis la //
NK048(tshi)001:1609: mi gnas blo las 'das pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1610: dbu ma yin la chen po'ang yin //
NK048(tshi)001:1611: ji srid res 'jog tshul gyis ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1612: ye shes de la ma reg par //
NK048(tshi)001:1613: rgyal ba kun gyi dgongs pa'i mthil //
NK048(tshi)001:1614: mthar thug dbu ma chen po min //
NK048(tshi)001:1615: gtsubs shing gtsubs pa'i me bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:1616: bden gnyis shes rab dri med kyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1617: drangs pa zung 'jug ye shes che //
NK048(tshi)001:1618: yod med yin min la sogs pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1619: mtha' bzhi'i spros kun nyer zhi ba'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1620: 'phags pa'i mnyam bzhag ye shes nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:1622: bden gnyis phyogs su ma lhung ba //
NK048(tshi)001:1623: de la rjes thob shes rab kyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1624: snang stong zung du 'jug pa zhes //
NK048(tshi)001:1625: brda' tsam sgo nas bzhag mod kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:1626: mnyam bzhag ye shes chen po'i ngor //
NK048(tshi)001:1627: snang dang stong dang zung 'jug gi /
NK048(tshi)001:1628: ngo bor dmigs su yod ma yin //
NK048(tshi)001:1629: snang ba tha snyad tshad ma'i yul //
NK048(tshi)001:1630: stong pa don dam dpyod pa'i yul //
NK048(tshi)001:1632: de rnams sgra rtog yul yin phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1633: de las 'das pa'i mnyam bzhag ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1634: so so rang gi ye shes tsam //
NK048(tshi)001:1635: snang bcas snang med la sogs kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:1636: de bzhin rig pas mi 'grub bo //
NK048(tshi)001:1637: des na ji srid res 'jog gi /
NK048(tshi)001:1638: bden gnyis bsgom pa shes rab ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1639: nam zhig res 'jog med par yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1640: zung 'jug ye shes thob pa'i tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:1641: phung po dgag bya rnam dpyad kyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1642: bcad pa'i med dgag stong rkyang las //
NK048(tshi)001:1644: tshul du so sor mi snang ba //
NK048(tshi)001:1645: snang cha thabs kyi rnam pa dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1646: ldan pa rnam kun mchog ldan gyi //
NK048(tshi)001:1647: stong nyid spros bral chen po dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1648: lhan skyes phyag rgya chen po sogs //
NK048(tshi)001:1649: mtshan gyi rnam grangs mang mnga' ba //
NK048(tshi)001:1650: sems 'das ye shes yin pa'i phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1651: rtog pa gzhan gyis bsam mi khyab //
NK048(tshi)001:1652: de ni sgra rtog yul min phyir //
NK048(tshi)001:1653: med dgag ma yin dgag sogs dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1654: tha dad dang ni snang stong sogs //
NK048(tshi)001:1655: ris su chad pa med pa ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1656: rgya chad phyogs lhung bral bas na //
NK048(tshi)001:1657: khas len yod med las 'das kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:1658: e wam zung du zhugs pa yi //
NK048(tshi)001:1659: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK048(tshi)001:1660: de ltar khas len las 'das pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1661: sgro skur dang bral dam pa'i don //
NK048(tshi)001:1664: 'on kyang bsam min byed po ltar //
NK048(tshi)001:1665: su yis rtogs med ma yin te //
NK048(tshi)001:1666: dri med rig pas dpyad pa yis //
NK048(tshi)001:1667: rab drang so so rang rig pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1668: rjes las thob pa'i ye shes kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:1669: nges shes chos kyi mar me ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1670: the tshom smag dang bral ba dag /
NK048(tshi)001:1671: mngon sum snang ba yod phyir ro //
NK048(tshi)001:1672: mdo lam thabs dang shes rab gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1673: gcig la gcig gis rtsis zin par //
NK048(tshi)001:1674: byed kyi 'dir ni thabs shes nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:1676: spros bral dbu ma chen po dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1677: 'od gsal rdzogs pa chen po gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1678: don gcig ming gi rnam grangs te //
NK048(tshi)001:1679: de las lhag pa'i lta ba med //
NK048(tshi)001:1680: gang phyir snang stong res 'jog tu //
NK048(tshi)001:1681: 'dzin med mtha' bzhi'i spros pa dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1682: bral phyir de las gzhan gyur na //
NK048(tshi)001:1683: spros dang bcas pa nyid phyir ro //
NK048(tshi)001:1685: dpyad bas gtan la phab pa nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:1686: sngags su rang gi rig dbyings su //
NK048(tshi)001:1687: thad kar myong bas grub pa yin //
NK048(tshi)001:1688: de phyir dbu ma zhes pa yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1689: bden gnyis so sor dpyod pa yi //
NK048(tshi)001:1690: shes rab lam gyi dbu ma dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1691: des drangs bden gnyis ro gcig pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1693: rgyu 'bras mdo sngags lta ba ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1694: snga ma shes rab cha yin la //
NK048(tshi)001:1695: phyi ma ye shes kho na yin //
NK048(tshi)001:1696: de phyir phyi ma 'di la ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1697: chen po'i sgra yis khyad du basngagasa //
NK048(tshi)001:1698: gnas lugs la yang de bzhin du //
NK048(tshi)001:1699: dngos po stong pa'i gnas lugs dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1700: bden gnyis dbyer med gnas lugs gnyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1701: ming gcig na yang don la ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1702: khyad par gnam sa bzhin du mchis //
NK048(tshi)001:1703: de bzhin chos nyid chos dbyings dang //
NK048(tshi)001:1704: stong nyid spros bral 'gog pa'i mtha' //
NK048(tshi)001:1705: don dam la sogs sgra mtshungs kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:1706: mthar thug dang ni nyi tshe ba'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1707: khyad par che phyir skabs so sor //
NK048(tshi)001:1708: phye nas ma nor bshad bya ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1709: sen+d+ha pa yi sgra bzhin no //
NK048(tshi)001:1710: de ltar zab mo'i dri ba bdun //
NK048(tshi)001:1711: zab rgyas don can tshig rnams kyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1712: bkrol tshe dri ba po de yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1713: gus bcas ngag gis 'di skad du //
NK048(tshi)001:1714: kye ma khron pa'i chu la rus sbal bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:1715: gzhan gzhung chos kyi rgya mtsho chen po'i 'jings //
NK048(tshi)001:1716: ma mthong rang bzhed khron pas dregs pa'i ro //
NK048(tshi)001:1717: myang ldan bdag cag khengs pa gtam 'dis bsnyil //
NK048(tshi)001:1718: rong klong zhes grags 'jam dpal dgyes pa'i gar //
NK048(tshi)001:1719: 'phags mchog thugs kyi rgya mtsho chen po na //
NK048(tshi)001:1720: sna tshogs nor bu'i chos mdzod mang mnga' ba //
NK048(tshi)001:1721: de spangs gzhan lugs 'ching bur re rnams 'khrul //
NK048(tshi)001:1722: chosa bazanga rig pas rnam dpyad bsam pa can //
NK048(tshi)001:1723: rtag tu bdud kyi bar chad byed pa med //
NK048(tshi)001:1724: de phyir rig lam seng ge'i sgra bo che //
NK048(tshi)001:1725: bsgrags pas mtsho skyes bstan pa'i rang lugs kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:1726: khyad par mchog la yid ches rnyed gyur cing //
NK048(tshi)001:1727: phyogs res dregs pa'i gzhan phyogs sun 'byin pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1728: mi 'phrog shes rab ral gri'i yu ba la //
NK048(tshi)001:1729: brten pa'i go skabs gzhan la sbyin par mdzod //
NK048(tshi)001:1730: chos tshul thos pa bdud rtsi'i mtsho 'dra la //
NK048(tshi)001:1731: zab mo'i don gang de yi nor bu bzhin /
NK048(tshi)001:1732: de dag gang na gnas kyang blang bya ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1733: ltar snang gang zag rjes su 'brang mi bya //
NK048(tshi)001:1734: mang thos mang du smra bas kyang min la //
NK048(tshi)001:1735: skyes sbyang zab zab ltar snang dpyad pas kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:1736: mi phigs zab don sa 'og gter 'dra ba //
NK048(tshi)001:1737: gang gis 'di 'dzin blo ldan nyid du shes //
NK048(tshi)001:1738: blo gter 'bum phrag nor bu'i snod nyid du //
NK048(tshi)001:1739: bdag blo zab yangs rgya mtsho cher bsgrubs pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1740: gdams pa'i legs byas slong ba'i dus rig nas //
NK048(tshi)001:1741: klu dbang dpal gyi rgya mtshor dga' bzhin 'thungs //
NK048(tshi)001:1742: gang las babs pa'i legs bshad chu klung gis //
NK048(tshi)001:1743: rnam dpyod blo yi rgya mtsho khyon yangs par //
NK048(tshi)001:1744: nges rtogs de yi 'byung gnas klu dbang ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1745: rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i zhal lung nyid du rtogs //
NK048(tshi)001:1746: mkha' mtha' hub kyis 'dren cing zos pa'i bcud //
NK048(tshi)001:1747: snying la kun phan bdud rtsi'i dpyid nyid du //
NK048(tshi)001:1748: len pa'i mthu chen blo la thob mdzad pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1749: ngo mtshar chos kyi mar me gsal bar mdzod //
NK048(tshi)001:1750: de skad zer zhing gus btud tshe //
NK048(tshi)001:1751: drang srong de yis de la yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1752: zab min zab rgyas su bsgrubs pa //
NK048(tshi)001:1753: gong gi don bsdus 'di ltar gdams //
NK048(tshi)001:1754: chos mchog seng ge'i 'o ma ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1755: blo gros snod bzang kho nas 'dzin //
NK048(tshi)001:1756: gzhan du 'bad kyang mi gnas ltar //
NK048(tshi)001:1758: a ni ma skyes chos kyi sgo //
NK048(tshi)001:1759: ra ni rdul dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK048(tshi)001:1760: pa ni don dam snang ba'i sgo //
NK048(tshi)001:1762: na ni ming dang bral ba nyid //
NK048(tshi)001:1763: d+h+aihni blo gros zab mo'i sgo //
NK048(tshi)001:1764: sgo drug de dag re re yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1765: bden gnyis tshul gyis dmigs nas su //
NK048(tshi)001:1766: sgyu ma'i ting 'dzin bsgrubs byas na //
NK048(tshi)001:1767: mtha' med rgya mtsho chen po'i chu //
NK048(tshi)001:1768: hub kyis lto ba 'dren nus pa'i //
NK048(tshi)001:1769: snying ga'i nor bu dri med la //
NK048(tshi)001:1770: gzungs spobs blo yi dpal du 'bar //
NK048(tshi)001:1771: mtha' bzhi'i spros pa khegs pa'i nges shes kyi //
NK048(tshi)001:1772: lam nas yin lugs gshis su son pa yi //
NK048(tshi)001:1773: blo las 'das pa 'od gsal gnyug ma'i dbyings //
NK048(tshi)001:1774: 'jam dpal rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang du zhog /
NK048(tshi)001:1775: mtha' bral lta ba'i rgyal po yangs pa'i klong //
NK048(tshi)001:1776: mnyam par bzhag pa'i bden don mthong ba las //
NK048(tshi)001:1777: mtha' bzhi'i blo ngan mun pa'i snang ba kun //
NK048(tshi)001:1778: ngang gis 'gags pa'i 'od gsal nyi ma 'char //
NK048(tshi)001:1779: gzur gnas dpyod pa drang srong ste //
NK048(tshi)001:1780: thol byung rtog pa ldom bu ba //
NK048(tshi)001:1781: de des dris lan tshul gyis ni //
NK048(tshi)001:1782: dka' gnas rgyal srid grangs ldan bshad //
NK048(tshi)001:1783: blo chung rtog ge bdag 'dra yis //
NK048(tshi)001:1784: shin tu zab cing barlinga ba'i don //
NK048(tshi)001:1785: blo chen 'phags pa'i thugs nas kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:1786: blangs pa bzhin du 'di na bkod //
NK048(tshi)001:1787: de skad smras pa'i legs bshad chos kyi char //
NK048(tshi)001:1788: rgyal sras bye bas bgrod cing dga' bzhin gyis //
NK048(tshi)001:1789: mnyan pas don chen thob par sems pa yis //
NK048(tshi)001:1790: dris la yi rangs bdud rtsi'i go skabs dbye //
NK048(tshi)001:1791: de phyir de bas de ltar yang dang yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1792: zab rgyas don sems du ma'i don du yang //
NK048(tshi)001:1793: yid kyi me long ngos la ji shar bzhin //
NK048(tshi)001:1794: rtsed 'jo'i rol pas d+h+aihminga can gyis spel //
NK048(tshi)001:1795: bde gshegs chos tshul zab mo nam mkha'i mtha' //
NK048(tshi)001:1796: rnam pa kun tu brjod par mi nus kyang //
NK048(tshi)001:1797: nges shes rin po che yi sgron me 'dir //
NK048(tshi)001:1798: brten na theg mchog lam bzang rnyed par nus //
